{"1":[[2110,2310,"Emily, this is plagiarism."],[2310,2506,"You are supposed to be the youngest,"],[2506,2736,"most talented hacker in the nation."],[2761,2873,"How could you cheat?"],[2919,3032,"I didn't cheat."],[3032,3111,"Didn't you?"],[3182,3399,"100% similarity."],[3420,3595,"Plagiarism confirmed."],[3611,3787,"Cheater!"],[3845,4020,"Cheater!"],[4087,4262,"Cheater!"],[4337,4587,"We compared your code with Olivia's,"],[4587,4683,"line for line."],[4683,4829,"They are identical."],[4829,4929,"I really expected more"],[4929,5055,"from the genius hacker girl"],[5055,5105,"who breached"],[5105,5263,"the Pentagon multiple times."],[5296,5463,"Was that just built on lies too?"],[5518,5626,"I didn't cheat."],[5647,5772,"She's the one who copied me."],[5772,5951,"Emily, we're sisters."],[5951,6076,"How could you copy me?"],[6101,6181,"You've embarrassed"],[6181,6352,"the entire Hendricks family."],[6973,7111,"Look, you have to believe me, I-"],[7465,7607,"Your sister is right."],[7607,7728,"How can you embarrass us"],[7728,7803,"like this?"],[7803,7995,"Don't you know that this competition"],[7995,8124,"concerns the US-China"],[8124,8262,"Cybersecurity Agreement?"],[8291,8550,"The whole world is watching."],[8579,8767,"And you've just turned our family"],[8767,9004,"into a global laughingstock."],[9113,9296,"Why do you keep taking Olivia's side?"],[9334,9421,"I'm your real daughter."],[9421,9555,"Can you believe me once?"],[9555,9613,"Enough."],[9613,9859,"If you won't admit that you cheated"],[9876,10118,"and apologize for your wrongdoings,"],[10210,10339,"then I'll beat it out of you."],[10531,10585,"Dad."],[10668,10819,"So what if you're their daughter?"],[10856,10973,"In this family,"],[11011,11182,"I always win."],[12049,12216,"But I really didn't cheat."],[12270,12395,"So how did this happen?"],[12550,12679,"Oh, I know you didn't."],[12741,12854,"But, didn't you ever wonder"],[12854,12983,"how my code always ended up a"],[12983,13100,"perfect match to yours?"],[13113,13242,"perfect match to yours."],[13246,13396,"perfect match to yours."],[14214,14335,"Welcome, everyone."],[14364,14443,"The International"],[14443,14568,"Hacker Championship"],[14577,14810,"will begin in five minutes."],[14810,14864,"Wait."],[14864,15040,"Was I sent back in time"],[15094,15290,"before the hacking competition?"]],"2":[[283,546,"Hey, are you even listening to me?"],[567,696,"I said this competition"],[696,796,"means everything"],[796,975,"to Olivia and this family."],[1013,1130,"If you even think"],[1130,1284,"about copying off her again,"],[1330,1438,"I'll make sure you regret it."],[1480,1580,"The universe is giving me"],[1580,1672,"a second chance."],[1697,1860,"Last time I couldn't defend myself"],[1860,1964,"against their accusations,"],[1964,2072,"but this time I can."],[2131,2210,"Emily."],[2210,2464,"Don't touch me."],[2506,2669,"Dad, don't get your hopes up."],[2677,2898,"She's hopelessly addicted to cheating."],[2902,3019,"She'll never change."],[3023,3253,"If I'd known you were such a nasty brat,"],[3253,3349,"I would have never brought you"],[3349,3511,"back from that foster family."],[3511,3632,"And I never should have agreed"],[3632,3699,"to come back."],[3728,3841,"Then maybe I wouldn't be stuck"],[3841,3978,"in this loveless hellhole."],[4029,4187,"Watch your mouth, you ungrateful-"],[4187,4262,"Emily."],[4462,4567,"I know you hate me"],[4592,4750,"because you think I stole the love"],[4750,5009,"from Mom, Dad, and our brothers."],[5067,5292,"But, it's not my fault you got lost"],[5292,5467,"in foster care all those years."],[5513,5830,"If you want, I can leave."],[6056,6151,"Oh, don't worry."],[6252,6348,"With a family like this,"],[6348,6443,"who needs enemies?"],[6506,6585,"You can keep them."],[6635,6752,"Are you talking down to us?"],[6956,7040,"I sure am."],[7082,7157,"You all never believed"],[7157,7298,"a word I said."],[7298,7386,"Not once."],[7419,7545,"You play favorites."],[7549,7749,"You compare me to everyone I'm not."],[7778,7928,"And I'm always the one left out."],[7978,8116,"I was never family to you,"],[8116,8212,"just an outsider."],[8229,8408,"Emily, don't take it out on Damien."],[8512,8596,"It's my fault."],[8658,8779,"I was never meant to be"],[8779,8900,"a part of this family."],[8996,9171,"I'm not even their real daughter."],[9234,9388,"I don't deserve their love."],[9509,9663,"If you're mad, then..."],[9872,9964,"take it out on me."],[10043,10105,"Hit me."],[10264,10418,"Well, since you asked so nicely."]],"3":[[304,462,"How dare you hit Olivia-"],[600,713,"So what if I did?"],[759,875,"If anyone else tries me,"],[905,1009,"I'll give it to them too."],[1009,1292,"You ungrateful, useless brat."],[1305,1568,"I wish I never gave birth to you."],[1589,1851,"I wish Olivia was my real daughter."],[1939,2168,"Apologize for hitting your sister."],[2168,2252,"Now!"],[2419,2565,"You think I want you to be my mom?"],[2610,2702,"You think I want to be"],[2702,2802,"part of your family?"],[2852,2986,"I'm not going to apologize."],[2994,3123,"Because I didn't do anything wrong."],[3144,3269,"Stop it, brat."],[3286,3390,"Won't apologize?"],[3499,3636,"Then I'll beat it out of you."],[3887,3958,"Thanks."],[4250,4308,"Dad."],[4738,4804,"You know what?"],[4833,4929,"You lost the right to tell me"],[4929,5063,"what to do a long time ago."],[5138,5334,"I don't owe any of you anything."],[5380,5584,"How dare you disobey me?"],[5601,5689,"I'm your father."],[5709,5885,"Fathers are supposed to love"],[5897,6035,"and protect their daughters."],[6068,6164,"I only came back because"],[6164,6314,"you're my biological parents."],[6314,6423,"But you have ignored me"],[6423,6510,"from day one."],[6573,6735,"You let Olivia torment me."],[6865,6994,"You always choose her."],[7019,7086,"Now, since I'm clearly"],[7086,7165,"unwanted here,"],[7382,7511,"I'm cutting ties with all of you."],[7724,7807,"Maybe I should just"],[7807,7916,"drop out of the competition."],[7966,8087,"You never should have entered"],[8087,8183,"in the first place."],[8220,8291,"It would have saved us"],[8291,8379,"all this embarrassment."],[8383,8479,"Exactly."],[8479,8650,"Plus, Olivia is just gonna win"],[8683,8842,"like she always does."],[8988,9109,"She can't drop out."],[9154,9255,"I need her!"],[9313,9367,"What?"],[9367,9417,"No!"],[9417,9513,"You can't drop out!"],[9672,9751,"I mean,"],[9822,9893,"Emily,"],[10051,10201,"what about all your hard work?"],[10222,10364,"Are you really going to let"],[10364,10560,"all your efforts go to waste?"],[10568,10781,"Didn't you say you wanted to win?"],[10806,10877,"Come on."],[10910,11077,"The competition is about to start."],[11111,11240,"You can't just give up now."],[11369,11611,"Hmm, judging by her reaction,"],[11661,11782,"she must already have a plan"],[11782,11878,"to steal my code."],[11907,12012,"Sorry, Olivia."],[12041,12124,"This time,"],[12124,12299,"I'm taking back everything"],[12299,12395,"that was mine."]],"4":[[392,471,"Emily's acting like"],[471,608,"a completely different person."],[625,750,"She won't listen to any of you"],[750,834,"and she's threatening"],[834,934,"to cut ties with us."],[1013,1172,"She used to be so obedient."],[1172,1347,"She's just trying to stir up the drama"],[1347,1480,"to steal your spotlight."],[1522,1589,"Don't worry."],[1626,1726,"Once you win,"],[1801,1943,"we'll put her right back in her place."],[2135,2256,"Audience members,"],[2256,2485,"please head to the observation zone."],[2519,2748,"The competition is about to begin."],[2957,3115,"You got this, Olivia."],[3174,3290,"Go get 'em, tiger."],[4120,4266,"Welcome, everyone"],[4266,4366,"to this year's"],[4366,4512,"International Hackathon"],[4512,4617,"Championship."],[4650,4813,"It is an honor"],[4817,5034,"to stand before the brightest minds"],[5034,5167,"of your generation."],[5201,5438,"You are the future innovators"],[5438,5626,"who will reshape the tech world."],[6206,6314,"This year's theme"],[6335,6594,"is cybersecurity and defense."],[6614,6685,"Now,"],[6715,6986,"let's unveil today's challenges."],[7048,7253,"First up, an old favorite."],[7253,7386,"Challenge A:"],[7440,7565,"Capture the Flag."],[7703,7874,"And Challenge B:"],[7920,8108,"Celestial Security."],[8270,8337,"Now,"],[8375,8591,"select your battlefields."],[8591,8700,"In my last life,"],[8700,8908,"I put all my effort into Challenge A,"],[8908,9000,"but it didn't matter."],[9054,9171,"Olivia still copied me"],[9171,9288,"and framed me for cheating."],[9342,9417,"I'm not going to make the"],[9417,9530,"same mistake and choose"],[9530,9663,"the same challenge this time."],[9738,9864,"Celestial Security,"],[9893,10005,"no one's cracked that challenge"],[10005,10089,"in ten years."],[10126,10231,"It's all about hijacking"],[10231,10335,"satellite defenses."],[10377,10539,"Why don't I give it a try this time?"],[10931,11148,"Judges, Challenge B is about"],[11148,11365,"seizing control of a satellite, right?"],[11407,11528,"I know it's been unsolvable"],[11528,11640,"for ten years,"],[11661,11836,"but I'm ready to make history."],[12007,12195,"Emily, what about you?"],[12266,12383,"You won't choose the same track"],[12383,12562,"just to cheat off me again, will you?"],[12629,12725,"Why did she choose"],[12725,12896,"the exact same challenge as me"],[12946,13013,"again?"]],"5":[[45,141,"Why did she choose"],[141,304,"the exact same challenge as me"],[367,433,"again?"],[454,529,"Challenge B is not just"],[529,684,"some basic high school hack."],[684,771,"It's literally harder"],[771,975,"than breaking into air traffic control."],[975,1167,"No one's beaten it in over a decade"],[1167,1317,"and you think you can?"],[1317,1447,"Emily, are you really gonna"],[1447,1526,"pick Challenge B"],[1526,1701,"just to copy Olivia again?"],[1726,1872,"Don't go putting words in my mouth."],[1897,1997,"And just so you know,"],[2039,2181,"Challenge B is actually harder"],[2181,2364,"than hijacking a military base."],[2398,2456,"So,"],[2556,2640,"good luck with that."],[2698,2819,"I'll be choosing Challenge A."],[3165,3257,"From what I remember"],[3257,3370,"about Challenge A,"],[3370,3503,"the more creative the solution,"],[3503,3616,"the higher the score."],[3645,3837,"This time, I'll try three techniques."],[3866,4091,"Malware Analysis, Memory Tracing,"],[4091,4225,"and Symbolic Execution."],[4258,4429,"Try copying me now, Olivia."],[4542,4859,"Olivia, are you sure about Challenge B?"],[4859,5009,"There's still time to switch."],[5055,5284,"Actually, I was thinking of"],[5284,5409,"switching to Challenge A."],[5459,5588,"My plan is to implement"],[5588,5768,"three creative approaches."],[5780,6047,"Malware Analysis, Memory Tracing,"],[6047,6227,"and Symbolic Execution."],[6260,6343,"What the hell?"],[6364,6569,"How does she know my exact strategy?"]],"6":[[41,104,"Oops!"],[120,325,"Did I just give away my strategy?"],[350,529,"Emily, what's your plan?"],[571,746,"It's not the same as mine, right?"],[775,863,"Of course not."],[921,1059,"And this is a competition,"],[1059,1180,"not a group project."],[1205,1292,"So back off."],[1313,1388,"Emily."],[1476,1772,"How can you be so rude to your sister?"],[1780,1901,"Your foster parents"],[1901,2077,"never taught you any manners?"],[2106,2293,"Olivia would never be like you."],[2327,2590,"Even in competition, she's polite."],[2610,2698,"There it is again."],[2698,2844,"The constant comparison."],[2882,2952,"You treat her like"],[2952,3094,"she's some masterpiece,"],[3094,3232,"and I'm like this smudge"],[3232,3332,"you're trying to erase."],[3332,3470,"Guys, don't be mad."],[3553,3620,"She's right."],[3653,3787,"We're rivals after all."],[3832,4016,"I get why she has her guard up against me."],[4016,4179,"You're so selfish, Emily."],[4191,4337,"Olivia had no problem"],[4337,4508,"sharing her strategy with everyone."],[4537,4642,"If you're so ashamed"],[4642,4800,"of your half-baked idea,"],[4850,4963,"you should have just said so."],[4963,5055,"Everyone knows you're just gonna"],[5055,5226,"copy Olivia again."],[5309,5376,"You're not going to believe"],[5376,5501,"a word I say, are you?"],[5593,5697,"You know, thank you for showing me"],[5697,5830,"what family really means."],[5885,6006,"Absolutely nothing."],[6214,6468,"Guys, don't be so harsh."],[6489,6690,"We only have a short window to code."],[6698,6890,"Even if someone tried to copy me,"],[6890,7152,"they'd have to do it line for line."],[7173,7390,"And you wouldn't do that, right, Emily?"],[7436,7545,"Of course not."],[7791,7974,"Okay, looks like everyone's"],[7974,8145,"picked their battle stations."],[8174,8304,"Let the International"],[8304,8508,"Hacker Championship begin!"],[8858,8963,"I don't know how you"],[8963,9063,"manage to copy me."],[9096,9230,"But if I can't hide from you,"],[9250,9330,"then I might as well"],[9330,9451,"drop out of the competition."],[9484,9659,"Let's see you try to copy me now."],[9743,9843,"Excuse me, judges."],[9964,10064,"I'd like to withdraw"],[10064,10151,"from the competition."]],"7":[[41,162,"Excuse me, judges."],[258,367,"I'd like to withdraw"],[367,458,"from the competition."],[458,542,"What the hell?"],[542,625,"She's leaving?"],[625,746,"We just started."],[746,850,"So she's gonna give up"],[850,959,"just because she can't"],[959,1109,"plagiarize Olivia's code?"],[1142,1192,"Crap!"],[1217,1309,"If Emily drops out,"],[1309,1426,"what am I supposed to do?"],[1426,1551,"Excuse me, judges."],[1630,1776,"I said I'd like to withdraw."],[1810,2006,"The competition has already started."],[2006,2143,"You don't have to write"],[2143,2268,"a single line of code,"],[2268,2460,"but you will stay in your seat"],[2460,2565,"until time's up."],[3766,3983,"Why's Olivia not typing?"],[4020,4162,"What is she waiting for?"],[4283,4346,"Crap."],[4375,4512,"If I don't submit something,"],[4542,4592,"they'll figure out"],[4592,4721,"I've been bluffing all along."],[4758,4854,"I need an out."],[4875,4946,"Fast."],[5313,5442,"Sir, my chest."],[5476,5563,"It's tight."],[5593,5780,"I think I need medical assistance."],[5801,5860,"Easy."],[5860,6006,"We're going to get you checked out."],[6281,6373,"Focus, people."],[6373,6477,"Ten minutes left!"],[6644,6744,"Olivia's gone."],[6773,6844,"Which means"],[6844,6977,"she can't steal anything now."],[7044,7132,"Ten minutes."],[7148,7248,"That's plenty of time."],[8445,8500,"Perfect."],[8612,8767,"And with a few minutes to spare!"],[8796,8917,"I'm ready to submit."],[8983,9042,"What?"],[9088,9154,"Didn't you leave"],[9154,9267,"for medical assistance?"]],"8":[[50,225,"I thought you left for medical assistance."],[225,412,"Aw, Emily, you're so silly."],[446,604,"I got back five minutes ago."],[688,738,"No, what?"],[738,809,"How did you-"],[1255,1334,"Wow."],[1368,1514,"This is brilliant."],[1514,1559,"You know,"],[1559,1710,"I have judged hacking events"],[1710,1839,"for thirty years."],[1839,2052,"And I have never seen someone"],[2052,2223,"your age pull this off."],[2298,2448,"Especially how you cracked"],[2448,2585,"the X algorithm."],[2585,2719,"Oh, genius."],[2765,2882,"The X algorithm?"],[2894,3019,"Nobody's mastered that"],[3019,3190,"in the last ten years."],[3190,3361,"Olivia, how did you come up"],[3361,3457,"with this approach?"],[3482,3591,"Most people would follow"],[3591,3732,"conventional hacking methods"],[3732,3799,"to solve it."],[3820,3974,"But I wanted to challenge myself."],[3974,4191,"By using the faster and more difficult"],[4191,4312,"X algorithm."],[4333,4483,"Does that mean if Emily's code"],[4483,4642,"is identical to Olivia's,"],[4642,4917,"she's caught plagerizing in 4K?"],[5426,5613,"Cheater!"],[5643,5830,"She's a cheater!"],[5843,6076,"Cheater!"],[6097,6306,"They're accusing me of plagiarism again."],[6356,6552,"How can I escape this fate?"],[6677,6873,"Emily, I believe you."],[6915,7077,"If you submit your solution,"],[7077,7219,"and the system doesn't flag it"],[7219,7298,"for plagiarism,"],[7328,7428,"then you'll be washed clean"],[7428,7540,"of the allegations."],[7703,7849,"How about I give you a hand?"],[7932,7987,"Wait."],[8087,8162,"It actually looks like"],[8162,8387,"I've made a tiny mistake in my code."],[8500,8587,"Good thing the competition's"],[8587,8654,"not over yet."],[8654,8767,"I have time to fix it, right?"],[8796,8850,"What?"],[8921,9054,"You wrote the wrong code?"]],"9":[[33,179,"You wrote the wrong code?"],[450,529,"You wrote the wrong code."],[529,684,"Why didn't you say so earlier?"],[742,846,"Why are you freaking out?"],[900,942,"I'm the one"],[942,1051,"who made a mistake, right?"],[1155,1347,"Is it because you copied me?"],[1401,1514,"Mistakes and all?"],[1822,1972,"You're my sister."],[2022,2264,"I, I was just worried about your score."],[2364,2531,"Well, thank you so much"],[2531,2623,"for caring about me."],[2957,3107,"I really have to start fixing my code."],[3566,3649,"Sorry, Judge,"],[3649,3832,"but I also need to edit my code."],[3853,3924,"Are you sure?"],[3924,4133,"Your code looks perfect to me."],[4204,4391,"Emily's the real genius hacker here."],[4421,4550,"Once she edits her code,"],[4550,4704,"it'll definitely be even better."],[4758,4925,"I can't let her beat me."],[4954,5063,"I,"],[5063,5117,"I just thought"],[5117,5271,"I could make my code even better."],[5271,5355,"That's all."],[5384,5497,"But time's running out."],[5534,5672,"You'd better hurry, Miss Olivia."],[6202,6277,"Bitch."],[6289,6410,"What the hell are you doing?"],[6427,6606,"Why won't you hurry up and start typing?"],[6990,7115,"Didn't Olivia just say"],[7115,7261,"she wanted to edit her code?"],[7261,7432,"Why is she closing her laptop again?"],[7461,7657,"Olivia looks pretty nervous to me, but"],[7695,7866,"Emily's as cool as a cucumber."],[7949,8028,"What do you know?"],[8028,8162,"Olivia's a genius."],[8162,8345,"Geniuses have to visualize"],[8345,8516,"before they execute their plans."]],"10":[[204,325,"There's only one minute left."],[337,458,"If I start writing now,"],[458,542,"there's no way"],[542,679,"she'll have enough time to copy me."],[738,917,"And I'll make my code even better."],[1205,1284,"You idiot."],[1288,1514,"It doesn't matter how much time is left."],[1514,1639,"As long as you're typing,"],[1639,1839,"I'll catch up to you line for line."],[2373,2473,"I'm done editing."],[2569,2702,"Judge, I'm ready to submit."],[2781,2911,"Are you sure about that?"],[3090,3224,"Yes, I am."],[3737,4129,"Is that Shor's algorithm?"],[4250,4437,"Shor's algorithm?"],[4454,4533,"Olivia?"],[4558,4692,"A mere high school student"],[4704,4871,"was able to solve it?"],[4946,5234,"Well, Emily, how were your edits?"],[5263,5376,"You couldn't have possibly"],[5376,5476,"used Shor's Algorithm"],[5476,5568,"like I did, right?"],[5668,5801,"This is impossible."],[5801,5993,"I just finished my code seconds ago."],[5993,6172,"How did she manage to copy me again?"],[6222,6310,"Time to submit."],[7019,7086,"Now,"],[7178,7482,"let's see who the real copycat is."]],"11":[[308,579,"100% likelihood of plagiarism."],[900,1005,"Why is your code"],[1005,1197,"exactly the same as mine?"],[1217,1338,"How did she do this?"],[1418,1476,"She's right."],[1518,1785,"You used the same three-part strategy"],[1785,1893,"to capture the flag."],[1901,1972,"Emily,"],[2031,2218,"given that you submitted your code"],[2218,2348,"after Olivia's,"],[2348,2510,"I am sorry to say that"],[2510,2594,"you are now"],[2594,2815,"under suspicion of plagiarism."],[2844,3174,"Ma'am, I did not plagiarize anyone."],[3232,3582,"Plagiarizer! - Cheater!"],[3603,3720,"I can prove myself."],[3978,4108,"Let me take on Challenge B."],[4179,4287,"I can hack the satellite."],[4312,4371,"Crap."],[4371,4521,"If she succeeds with Challenge B,"],[4521,4704,"she'll become an overnight sensation."],[4704,4800,"And our family might start"],[4800,4921,"seeing her in a new light."],[4921,5030,"She'll steal my thunder."],[5130,5205,"Judges,"],[5276,5438,"I also want to take on Challenge B."],[5476,5584,"It's remained unsolved"],[5584,5659,"for a decade,"],[5659,5776,"but I think I can do it."],[5776,5951,"I want to push my limits."],[5951,6068,"And at the same time,"],[6135,6439,"I'll prove that I'm the real deal."],[6473,6564,"In that case,"],[6585,6852,"let's begin coding Challenge B."],[6886,7044,"Celestial Security."],[7044,7215,"The entire process will be"],[7215,7419,"monitored and live streamed."],[7440,7653,"We're leaving no room for plagiarism."],[7703,7761,"Olivia."],[7786,7841,"Emily."],[7878,7949,"Are you ready?"],[8379,8508,"She won't be able to copy me"],[8508,8641,"as long as I don't write anything."],[8671,8767,"I've also got a plan"],[8767,8846,"to prove my innocence"],[8846,8954,"when the time comes."],[9021,9271,"Now, let's start Challenge B."],[9930,10014,"Look at her hands"],[10014,10155,"fly across the keyboard."],[10155,10285,"Her code is streaming down"],[10285,10418,"like a waterfall."],[10418,10593,"This legendary challenge"],[10593,10769,"is going to be a walk in the park"],[10769,10852,"for Olivia."],[11048,11127,"What the hell?"],[11186,11344,"How is her code identical"],[11344,11461,"to the one in my mind?"],[11494,11599,"Could she really...?"]],"12":[[54,191,"No, that's crazy."],[221,396,"But how does she know exactly"],[396,475,"what I'm thinking?"],[500,571,"Emily?"],[604,725,"Why aren't you writing?"],[796,1034,"Are you waiting for me to finish"],[1034,1180,"so you can copy everything again?"],[1518,1593,"This is bad."],[1605,1714,"I should test her."],[1793,1914,"Emily, if you don't know"],[1914,2052,"how to hack the satellite,"],[2052,2156,"I can teach you."],[2156,2281,"But you have to promise"],[2281,2452,"to never plagiarize me again."],[2473,2706,"It's not just unfair to the other teams."],[2748,2936,"It's embarrassing for our whole family."],[2952,3098,"I never plagiarized you."],[3123,3294,"That was my code to begin with."],[3420,3616,"You're such a fucking joke, Olivia."],[3628,3862,"An idiotic braindead bimbo like you"],[3862,3978,"wants to steal my code?"],[3978,4087,"How dare you call me a"],[4087,4191,"braindead bimbo?"],[5305,5463,"She can really read my mind?"],[5463,5655,"Keep pretending, Olivia."],[5714,5784,"It won't be long"],[5784,5935,"before I rip that mask off"],[5935,6118,"and show everyone who you really are."]],"13":[[108,308,"Mr. Smith, how can I help you?"],[329,471,"I'm in the audience."],[496,775,"Oh, yes, I understand."],[804,955,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[967,1159,"we have a special viewer"],[1159,1284,"in the audience today."],[1322,1626,"A representative from the Pentagon"],[1626,1830,"has taken a special interest"],[1830,1935,"in today's satellite"],[1935,2064,"hacking competition."],[2102,2202,"The Pentagon?"],[2227,2435,"Whoever wins this is set for life."],[2464,2548,"That's right."],[2569,2761,"Whoever hacks the satellite first"],[2761,2877,"will be invited"],[2877,3174,"to the military's Quanta Project,"],[3174,3319,"our country's top"],[3319,3478,"cyber research program."],[3816,3991,"Have PR draft a statement now."],[4020,4233,"Once Olivia wins, the whole world"],[4233,4371,"is gonna know she's a Hendricks."],[4617,4696,"Don't worry, Dad."],[4729,4821,"I'm already on it."],[4859,5030,"Just imagine."],[5055,5192,"Once Olivia wins,"],[5192,5397,"our stocks will be soaring."],[5397,5613,"All our money worries will, poof,"],[5613,5814,"fade into thin air."],[6498,6560,"I'm done."],[7048,7132,"Didn't you say"],[7132,7286,"you wanted to do Challenge B?"],[7315,7369,"Why haven't you"],[7369,7494,"written anything yet, Emily?"],[7691,7907,"Right, I almost forgot."],[7945,8133,"You can't copy me now."],[8195,8420,"Not with everyone watching."],[8596,8687,"It must be hard trying"],[8687,8875,"to figure it all out by yourself, huh?"],[8883,9029,"I need to write a better version"],[9029,9163,"of the quote Olivia copied."],[9163,9259,"It's the only way"],[9259,9434,"to shut down the plagiarism claims."]],"14":[[408,600,"Emily should just quit already."],[600,709,"Why is she still sitting there"],[709,821,"like a damn statue?"],[821,896,"She's gonna embarrass"],[896,975,"the whole family."],[1017,1130,"See, Emily?"],[1130,1313,"Who cares if you're their real daughter?"],[1313,1564,"Mom and Dad will always take my side."],[1564,1722,"And soon, I'll rip that"],[1722,1914,"genius hacker title right off of you."],[2214,2293,"What do I do?"],[2302,2452,"She already copied my code."],[2452,2519,"I don't have time"],[2519,2690,"to write a new one from scratch."],[2694,2852,"Emily, better hurry up"],[2852,2927,"and write your code"],[2927,3044,"before the time runs out."],[3090,3153,"Ha."],[3178,3274,"Easier said than done."],[3274,3374,"I can't believe we're letting"],[3374,3570,"a plagiarizer like her participate."],[3570,3645,"She's bringing down"],[3645,3762,"everyone's reputation."],[3774,3862,"Exactly."],[3874,4008,"If she's gonna plagiarize,"],[4008,4166,"we should ban her from all events."],[4191,4300,"Ban her!"],[4316,4396,"Ban her!"],[4412,4537,"Ban her!"],[4537,4650,"Get her out of here!"],[4700,4804,"Ban her!"],[4838,4946,"Judges."],[4946,5050,"Listen to them."],[5050,5255,"Maybe it's time to..."],[5309,5509,"Emily, Challenge B is a tough one."],[5534,5647,"If you can't handle it,"],[5647,5818,"maybe it's best to just call it."],[6168,6293,"Who says I can't do it?"]],"15":[[425,517,"Guys."],[588,650,"Come on."],[667,738,"Be nice."],[738,825,"Give her some time."],[855,1017,"She's completely self-taught,"],[1017,1280,"so her process is different."],[1313,1393,"Who knows?"],[1447,1568,"Maybe she'll surprise us."],[1597,1739,"Even if she is good,"],[1739,1931,"is she good enough to hack a satellite?"],[1931,2039,"I don't think so."],[2039,2235,"Let's sit back and watch this fraud"],[2243,2344,"crash and burn."],[2369,2548,"Looks like Olivia's taking the win today."],[2556,2736,"Damien, release the PR statement."],[2744,2827,"The world needs to know"],[2827,2869,"she's a"],[2869,3048,"once-in-a-generation genius."],[3103,3299,"Can we wrap this up already?"],[3299,3420,"We don't have time"],[3420,3586,"for some cheater's drama."],[3616,3828,"Just announce the winner."],[4583,4654,"Alright."],[4708,4988,"The winner of the championship is..."],[5384,5447,"Wait."],[5472,5584,"Emily's coding."],[6827,6944,"Emily's code."],[6981,7173,"It's even better than Olivia's."]],"16":[[29,91,"No."],[104,166,"Wait."],[166,342,"She's breaking through the firewall."],[387,483,"Are you serious?"],[483,588,"Cracking that firewall"],[588,763,"is harder than breaching the NSA."],[763,909,"No way some copycat"],[909,1021,"could pull that off."],[1067,1180,"She can."],[1180,1372,"And she's close to succeeding, too."],[1593,1659,"Breaking into"],[1659,1864,"a military satellite firewall"],[1864,1968,"while still in high school?"],[1968,2122,"A genius indeed."],[2223,2302,"Oh, no."],[2352,2423,"She shouldn't be able"],[2423,2531,"to crack Challenge B."],[2531,2686,"Not with so little time left."],[2731,2873,"You see that man over there?"],[2890,3032,"The one in the military uniform?"],[3057,3265,"He's the leader of the Quanta Project."],[3290,3415,"Looks like Emily's already"],[3415,3507,"got his approval."],[4233,4475,"Did you really think I had no backup plan"],[4475,4658,"after you copied me, Olivia."],[4859,4913,"No."],[4929,5055,"I can't let her win."],[5055,5121,"Stop!"],[5121,5246,"That's my code."],[5338,5513,"Why do you keep copying me?"],[5572,5643,"Olivia."],[5689,5793,"What?"],[5805,6051,"Is she plagiarizing again?"]],"17":[[29,183,"Plagiarizer!"],[196,275,"Unbelievable."],[296,471,"Is she still copying Olivia?"],[471,692,"Olivia, the code that Emily just wrote..."],[729,813,"It's really yours?"],[838,896,"Yes."],[896,1071,"It's from a strategy I wrote"],[1071,1251,"way before the competition."],[1263,1351,"I don't know"],[1351,1505,"why Emily keeps copying me."],[1643,1735,"It's yours?"],[1764,1860,"Then why didn't you use it"],[1860,1947,"during the competition"],[1947,2006,"just now?"],[2043,2360,"This whole thing is being live-streamed."],[2394,2594,"Everyone saw Emily write her own code."],[2619,2756,"It doesn't look like yours at all."],[2894,2965,"Whatever."],[3019,3207,"I'm telling you, she stole it."],[3232,3328,"Do you have proof?"],[3374,3453,"I..."],[3511,3595,"I..."],[3632,3832,"Don't worry, sweetheart."],[3832,3991,"Mommy's right here."],[4004,4183,"Just show them your proof."],[4204,4325,"We got your back, Olivia."],[4350,4491,"Hey, isn't that Mr. Smith,"],[4491,4646,"the head of the Quanta Project?"],[4713,4892,"Well, Olivia, let's see"],[4892,5088,"how you talk your way out of this one?"],[5134,5201,"Ethan!"],[5255,5434,"Didn't you steal part of my code for her?"]],"18":[[20,112,"What?"],[112,225,"When did I ever-"],[287,367,"Wait."],[367,496,"Maybe Olivia has her reasons"],[496,592,"for saying that."],[592,658,"Yeah."],[709,975,"Emily told me to steal Olivia's code."],[975,1126,"She's the one plagiarizing."],[1159,1267,"She seriously tried"],[1267,1401,"to cheat on a livestream?"],[1401,1576,"My god, this Hacker Championship's"],[1576,1714,"about to blow up online."],[1922,1989,"Miss Emily,"],[2031,2189,"you've been accused of plagiarism."],[2252,2402,"What do you have to say for yourself?"],[2485,2827,"Mr. Smith, I swear I wrote that code"],[2827,2894,"by myself."],[2957,3032,"I promise."],[3069,3115,"And you're saying"],[3115,3286,"I had Ethan steal it for me?"],[3365,3457,"Where's your proof?"],[3470,3645,"I am so sick of this family."],[3674,3824,"And you, Miss Olivia?"],[3887,4020,"Any concrete evidence?"],[4045,4141,"Of course I do."],[4183,4462,"She only copied 60% of my code."],[4483,4617,"I can finish the rest right now"],[4617,4683,"to prove it."],[4913,5067,"Doesn't matter what you write."],[5088,5326,"I can copy anything you come up with."],[5326,5588,"You still have no idea, huh?"],[5609,5793,"As long as you're within six feet,"],[5793,6043,"I can read your mind."],[6068,6156,"Wait a second."],[6193,6364,"Every time she's copied me,"],[6368,6506,"she always tried to get closer"],[6506,6585,"to me first."],[6627,6740,"Does her mind reading power"],[6740,6865,"only work up close?"],[7565,7678,"What the hell is she doing?"],[7716,7811,"That's what I thought."],[7874,8024,"So if I keep my distance,"],[8041,8162,"you've got nothing on me."]],"19":[[408,450,"Wait."],[467,592,"Why is she backing away like that?"],[621,796,"Did she find out I can read minds?"],[813,984,"Well, since Olivia said"],[984,1184,"she can finish the last 40% of the code,"],[1238,1443,"please, go ahead."],[1747,1856,"Where are you going?"],[1856,1968,"Just stay where you are"],[1968,2102,"and write the rest of the code!"],[2118,2239,"She's getting nervous."],[2264,2456,"We've got a solid six feet between us now."],[2473,2619,"I bet that's the limit of her power."],[2656,2761,"This should be safe."],[2794,2944,"I've never told anyone"],[2944,3057,"that I can read minds."],[3103,3228,"There's no way this idiot"],[3228,3311,"could have figured it out."],[3399,3603,"I'm just giving you some space, Olivia."],[3641,3745,"That way, you won't be worried"],[3745,3891,"about me peeking over your shoulder."],[3912,4083,"Well, shouldn't you get to typing?"],[4270,4408,"I was just giving you the chance"],[4408,4533,"to apologize first."],[4612,4804,"As long as I admit to plagiarizing-"],[5017,5146,"As long as you admit"],[5146,5363,"to plagiarizing my code,"],[5392,5455,"then I'll,"],[5492,5638,"I'll ask our parents to"],[5638,5801,"accept you into the family."],[5843,5964,"Just write the code."],[6010,6126,"Unless you don't actually know"],[6126,6197,"how to do it."],[6268,6368,"That would basically prove"],[6368,6493,"that you copied me."]],"20":[[20,175,"Ethan saw me write it!"],[196,342,"I just didn't use it at first"],[342,467,"because our parents raised me"],[467,592,"not to be a show-off."],[592,717,"But I didn't expect Emily"],[717,942,"to keep copying me over and over."],[963,1230,"So that's why you took on Challenge B."],[1267,1413,"To steal from Olivia."],[1497,1580,"A disgrace."],[1618,1697,"Just admit it."],[1714,1856,"Say you plagiarized and apologize"],[1856,1989,"for wasting everyone's time."],[1997,2181,"Even her family is turning on her."],[2198,2339,"Maybe she really did do it."],[2364,2481,"That's so messed up."],[2510,2652,"She seriously tried to take on"],[2652,2727,"Challenge B"],[2727,2869,"without any skills?"],[2894,2994,"Shameless."],[3019,3078,"Get out."],[3119,3278,"We can't allow a plagiarizer"],[3278,3407,"into the Quanta Project."],[3420,3557,"Miss Emily, I'll need you"],[3557,3728,"to prove your innocence yourself."],[3728,3853,"What's there to prove?"],[3866,4049,"She's a serial copycat."],[4058,4133,"Don't worry, sir."],[4133,4275,"We're gonna take her home right now,"],[4291,4433,"and hopefully get the committee"],[4433,4579,"to ban her for good."],[4604,4717,"Ban her!"],[4733,4842,"Ban her!"],[4846,4942,"Ban her!"],[4954,5050,"Ban her!"],[5063,5150,"Ban her!"],[5155,5246,"Ban her!"],[5267,5321,"Ban her!"],[5321,5484,"Wait, what's the rush?"],[5543,5655,"Olivia said she could write"],[5655,5776,"the rest of the code, right?"],[5797,5922,"If she's successful,"],[5943,6101,"I'll admit I plagiarized her,"],[6101,6256,"apologize to everyone,"],[6256,6377,"and I'll never attend"],[6377,6539,"a hacking event again."],[6673,6894,"Hey, let's release a statement now."],[6936,7186,"Title it Genius Hacker Girl"],[7186,7353,"Caught Plagiarizing."],[7390,7640,"So, stop messing around"],[7661,7774,"and show us what you've got."],[7816,7870,"Fine."],[7891,7995,"If this is what it takes"],[7995,8112,"to convince Emily,"],[8137,8287,"then I'll write the rest of the code"],[8287,8400,"right in front of her."],[8445,8712,"Emily, sit tight and watch."]],"21":[[29,100,"Gotcha."],[116,258,"Now that you're within six feet,"],[258,412,"I can hear every single thought"],[412,483,"in your head."],[546,646,"Let's see,"],[696,925,"what's the last part of this code?"],[1197,1601,"A, b, c, d, e, f, g,"],[1601,1964,"h, i, j, k, l, m, n, o-"],[1964,2060,"What the hell are you singing?"],[2152,2189,"Singing?"],[2189,2235,"Me?"],[2289,2410,"I didn't sing anything."],[2489,2594,"What's going on?"],[2594,2752,"Hey, are you gonna code or what?"],[2752,2790,"Code!"],[2790,2865,"Just code."],[2865,2923,"Code!"],[2923,3032,"Code already!"],[3036,3086,"Just code."],[3094,3211,"Stop rushing me!"],[3549,3766,"Olivia, that was kind of rude."],[3795,3895,"I mean, you did say"],[3895,4004,"you were gonna finish the code,"],[4004,4054,"right?"],[4074,4233,"So, hurry up."],[4266,4325,"Get to it."],[4391,4642,"I've given you several chances, Emily."],[5167,5292,"The last part confirms"],[5292,5409,"the firewall breach."],[5422,5572,"Once it detects vulnerability,"],[5605,5759,"then I'll take control remotely"],[5759,5918,"using radio signals."],[6202,6322,"You really thought"],[6322,6452,"singing could stop me?"],[6485,6664,"As long as I can trigger the logic"],[6690,6810,"linked to the existing code"],[6810,6873,"in your brain,"],[6894,7090,"I can copy it just like before."]],"22":[[329,412,"She's right."],[475,654,"First you breach the firewall,"],[663,775,"then use radio."],[875,1096,"We wish you a merry Christmas."],[1105,1334,"We wish you a merry Christmas."],[1355,1539,"And the last line is..."],[1539,1780,"We wish you a merry Christmas."],[1780,1922,"And a happy new year!"],[2569,2769,"What the hell is wrong with you?"],[2848,2977,"And why are you singing"],[2977,3065,"a Christmas song"],[3065,3128,"in your head"],[3128,3265,"of all things?"],[3278,3424,"What are you talking about, Olivia?"],[3424,3528,"A Christmas song?"],[3678,3866,"Anyway, get back to it."],[3966,4054,"Time's ticking."],[4312,4504,"This stupid trick won't work forever."],[4504,4646,"I'll still win in the end."]],"23":[[54,308,"Jingle bells, jingle bells,"],[308,513,"jingle all the way."],[542,784,"Deck the halls with boughs of Holly."],[784,1038,"Fa la la la la la la la la."],[1042,1184,"On the first day of Christmas"],[1184,1351,"my true love gave to me"],[1351,1609,"a partridge in a pear tree."],[1730,1881,"Is she a literal idiot?"],[1881,1956,"Why is her mind"],[1956,2047,"filled with these stupid"],[2047,2164,"Christmas songs?"],[2164,2223,"Ugh!"],[2223,2314,"Did she find out"],[2314,2452,"that I can read her mind?"],[2548,2656,"Is she singing on purpose"],[2656,2765,"to interfere with me?"],[2802,2848,"No."],[2940,3015,"There's no way she could have"],[3015,3073,"found out."],[3123,3349,"Miss Olivia, please be mindful"],[3349,3511,"of everyone's valuable time."],[3566,3782,"Will you finish the code or not?"],[3828,3924,"Of course I can."],[3962,4058,"I was the one who wrote it"],[4058,4149,"in the first place."],[4166,4341,"Olivia, you still haven't"],[4341,4562,"written a single line of code."],[4592,4700,"Are you still pretending"],[4700,4808,"that you didn't copy me?"],[4942,5067,"So what if I did?"],[5100,5280,"As long as I don't admit it,"],[5309,5684,"you can't do anything."],[5789,5855,"Oh, yeah?"]],"24":[[120,287,"How dare you hit Olivia!"],[346,404,"Shh."],[479,558,"Keep it down."],[558,625,"You don't want to ruin"],[625,800,"Olivia's big moment, do you?"],[1176,1272,"And you two!"],[1292,1347,"What the hell"],[1347,1455,"are you still doing up here?"],[1514,1601,"Where's security?"],[1951,2077,"You already stole my family."],[2189,2364,"And now you want to take everything"],[2364,2469,"that I've worked for?"],[2531,2631,"Not a chance."],[2702,2977,"If you can't finish that code, I will."],[3278,3482,"I didn't copy you!"],[3507,3670,"You plagiarized me!"],[3670,3749,"Then prove it!"],[3791,3887,"Finish the code!"],[3970,4320,"Miss Olivia, do you or do you not know"],[4320,4466,"how to write the remaining code?"],[4491,4596,"Of course I do!"],[4646,4717,"I was the one"],[4717,4854,"who wrote it in the first place!"],[4879,5038,"Then please prove yourself."],[5063,5150,"Prove yourself!"],[5163,5288,"Prove yourself!"],[5359,5563,"Prove yourself!"],[5613,5734,"You know, if you can't actually write it,"],[5734,5997,"then just tell us the logic behind it."],[5997,6093,"That works too."],[6110,6227,"Has she really been bluffing"],[6227,6318,"this whole time?"]],"25":[[120,237,"When I was being passed around"],[237,329,"foster homes,"],[367,633,"I entered every coding competition"],[633,679,"I could find."],[734,855,"And I won all of them."],[884,1005,"So what gives you the right"],[1005,1176,"to say that I plagiarized you?"],[1197,1301,"I'm telling the truth!"],[1301,1409,"You copied me!"],[1434,1572,"I'll set the record straight today."],[1609,1755,"Olivia can't finish the code"],[1755,1918,"because she's the copycat."],[1939,2173,"And if by some miracle she finishes it,"],[2214,2364,"I'll admit that I copied her."],[2631,2957,"Emily, stop acting so full of yourself."],[2973,3153,"Olivia's been trying to save you"],[3153,3395,"from embarrassment all day."],[3407,3607,"If she actually finishes the code,"],[3641,3716,"you're done."],[3749,3908,"Well, then you better beg"],[3908,4033,"that precious daughter of yours"],[4033,4133,"to finish the code."],[4133,4266,"Otherwise when the truth comes out,"],[4287,4446,"it won't be my life that's ruined."],[4462,4546,"It'll be hers."],[4608,4675,"Oh, right."],[4738,4821,"You guys already issued"],[4821,4971,"that press release, didn't you?"],[4988,5092,"After Challenge A?"],[5117,5196,"Stating that Olivia"],[5196,5338,"is some hacker genius?"],[5372,5513,"So if she's not able to finish it,"],[5513,5638,"that's gonna look really bad"],[5638,5739,"for business,"],[5739,5818,"won't it?"],[5922,6143,"You ungrateful brat."]],"26":[[58,291,"Emily, I know you've held a grudge"],[291,462,"ever since Mom and Dad got you back"],[462,592,"from the foster home"],[592,750,"and never went public about it."],[771,1005,"But framing me for plagiarism"],[1026,1172,"to get back at our family?"],[1230,1355,"That's messed up!"],[1401,1468,"Oh?"],[1468,1614,"You want to pressure me into coding?"],[1634,1718,"Nice try."],[1735,1856,"But I've got a hundred ways"],[1856,1943,"to get out of this."],[2089,2198,"You better stop it"],[2198,2381,"with that fake-ass tone."],[2581,2719,"Emily, are you insane?"],[3161,3440,"My apologies, everyone."],[3461,3586,"As head of this family,"],[3586,3712,"I take full responsibility"],[3712,3870,"for this plagiarism scandal."],[3920,4049,"I will take Emily home"],[4079,4254,"and handle this immediately."],[4275,4562,"Olivia, sweetheart, are you alright?"],[4971,5059,"I'm fine."],[5163,5442,"If hurting me makes Emily happy,"],[5442,5568,"then I'll take it."],[5605,5751,"But I can't just stand by"],[5751,5926,"while she goes down the wrong path."],[5960,6085,"It hurts being accused"],[6085,6218,"of something I didn't do."],[6260,6443,"I wrote that code."],[6468,6564,"And now she's saying"],[6564,6715,"I stole you guys too?"],[6744,6894,"It's obvious she doesn't want me"],[6894,7027,"to be a part of this family."],[7073,7319,"Apologize to Olivia right now."],[7444,7595,"She's obviously lying."],[7615,7757,"Why should I apologize?"],[7924,8099,"Still denying it in front of everyone."],[8145,8258,"If we hadn't caught it,"],[8299,8412,"who knows what you'd still be doing"],[8412,8475,"to Olivia?"],[8696,8871,"So I slap her once"],[8871,8971,"and you call that bullying."],[9038,9138,"What about all the crap"],[9138,9296,"that she pulled on me, huh?"],[9505,9638,"Where were all of you?"],[9638,9822,"Why didn't anyone speak up for me?"]],"27":[[108,337,"Emily, accusing me of plagiarism"],[337,450,"is bad enough,"],[450,533,"but abuse?"],[533,600,"Really?"],[600,863,"Mom, Dad, you know I'd never do that."],[880,984,"It's okay, darling."],[1034,1126,"We're your parents."],[1126,1234,"Of course we believe you."],[1288,1514,"So you're saying that I made this,"],[1539,1676,"that I made all of this up?"],[1676,1851,"Look, it's bad enough that you're always"],[1851,1956,"going after Olivia's stuff,"],[1956,2077,"but did you have to do this"],[2077,2218,"on a global livestream?"],[2252,2398,"Can you not embarrass"],[2398,2510,"the family like this?"],[2677,2719,"You know what?"],[2719,2811,"If I'll never be good enough"],[2811,2890,"for this family,"],[2915,2994,"then forget it."],[3044,3136,"I'm done trying."],[3269,3378,"It's all my fault."],[3474,3578,"I know you hate sharing"],[3578,3695,"our family's love with me."],[3728,3874,"So make up for it."],[3933,4116,"I'll leave the Hendricks family."],[4233,4316,"And I'll also"],[4316,4475,"drop out of the competition."],[5000,5188,"Coding means everything to you."],[5221,5380,"How can you just give it up?"],[5426,5543,"Stop pretending!"],[5551,5709,"If you're gonna leave, then just go!"],[5914,6018,"If I knew"],[6018,6151,"you'd turn out this vicious,"],[6151,6310,"I never would have brought you home."],[6335,6381,"Yeah?"],[6381,6468,"Well, I don't want a family"],[6468,6610,"that keeps playing favorites."],[6648,6756,"Listen up, everyone."],[6831,6931,"As of this moment,"],[6931,7057,"I am officially done"],[7057,7169,"with the Hendricks family."],[7720,7820,"And as for that code,"],[7924,8220,"I'm not letting you get away that easily."]],"28":[[62,333,"I'm not letting you get away that easily."],[354,425,"Oh, right."],[446,638,"Olivia still hasn't finished the code."],[658,846,"Honestly, the longer she stalls,"],[846,967,"the worse it looks."],[1038,1101,"No."],[1159,1418,"Olivia's obviously trying to save Emily"],[1418,1530,"the embarrassment."],[1543,1789,"Olivia hasn't proved her innocence yet."],[1810,1872,"Right now,"],[1872,2010,"we're going off her word for it."],[2010,2135,"We can't confirm"],[2135,2327,"if she really wrote the original code."],[2327,2519,"Olivia, hurry up and write it!"],[2519,2615,"Prove to everyone that"],[2615,2761,"Emily's the one that cheated here."],[2827,2890,"I..."],[2923,3015,"Listen up, everyone."],[3044,3161,"I swear right now,"],[3161,3249,"in front of all of you,"],[3286,3499,"that if Olivia finishes the code,"],[3516,3657,"I will admit I plagiarized"],[3657,3778,"and never code again"],[3778,3891,"for the rest of my life."],[4087,4320,"Emily sounds really confident."],[4329,4471,"Maybe she's really innocent."],[4471,4650,"Well, since Emily"],[4650,4775,"put it out there already,"],[4775,5017,"I don't need to show her any more mercy."],[5059,5146,"Go, Olivia."],[5167,5246,"Prove her wrong."],[5271,5367,"Prove it!"],[5392,5492,"Prove it!"],[5505,5597,"Prove it!"],[5622,5726,"Prove it!"],[5730,5805,"Prove it!"],[5814,5930,"Prove it!"],[5976,6051,"Prove it!"],[6060,6143,"Prove it!"],[6214,6281,"Prove it!"],[6297,6385,"Prove it!"],[6398,6510,"Prove it!"],[6598,6652,"Olivia!"],[6660,6694,"Olivia."],[7182,7278,"Did she faint?"],[7278,7344,"No way."],[7374,7478,"What just happened?"],[7678,7724,"Wow."],[7724,7874,"Playing the sick card now,"],[7874,7928,"are we?"]],"29":[[333,525,"Everyone, there's been an accident."],[525,646,"We are pausing the event"],[646,742,"until further notice."],[742,871,"Please remain calm."],[1067,1251,"Judges, since she didn't finish"],[1251,1313,"that code,"],[1351,1426,"doesn't that prove"],[1426,1534,"that I didn't plagiarize?"],[1568,1689,"For God's sake!"],[1689,1793,"Olivia almost passed out"],[1793,1856,"and here you are"],[1856,1997,"still whining about the code?"],[2035,2122,"Seriously."],[2152,2318,"Is winning a silly competition"],[2318,2485,"more important than your sister's life?"],[2540,2681,"I'll never acknowledge"],[2681,2827,"a selfish bully like you"],[2827,2915,"as my daughter."],[3023,3069,"Yeah?"],[3123,3203,"Well, I will never"],[3203,3274,"acknowledge a family"],[3274,3436,"that plays double standards like this."],[3457,3624,"When I want to win, you call me selfish,"],[3624,3712,"but when she wants to win,"],[3712,3853,"you treat her like some kind of hero."],[4079,4166,"If I would have fainted,"],[4166,4250,"would you even care?"],[4512,4654,"Judges, let me finish the code."],[4675,4825,"I promise I didn't plagiarize."],[4871,4929,"No!"],[5130,5251,"That's enough for today."],[5292,5484,"The competition will resume in one week."],[5526,5618,"We'll settle this then."],[5676,5743,"Alright."],[5743,5822,"First, please,"],[5822,5939,"let's get her to the hospital."],[6264,6427,"If anything happens to Olivia,"],[6448,6564,"we'll make you regret it."],[6681,6748,"Same here."],[6810,6894,"In seven days,"],[6915,7077,"I'll make Olivia regret everything."]],"30":[[166,254,"Oh, Mr. Smith!"],[275,350,"Please wait."],[467,675,"Mr. Smith is leading the Quanta Project."],[692,913,"If I can just join his research team,"],[913,1034,"no one will accuse me"],[1034,1159,"of being a plagiarizer."],[1205,1305,"What's the matter?"],[1305,1409,"I heard that the winner"],[1409,1539,"of the Hacker Championships"],[1539,1630,"will be offered a job"],[1630,1818,"at the Quanta Project research team."],[1872,1951,"Is that true?"],[1951,2068,"Why, yes it is."],[2118,2335,"I appreciate your interest, Miss."],[2385,2456,"But you're caught up"],[2456,2673,"in that plagiarism scandal right now."],[2698,2777,"Our team is made up of"],[2777,2911,"real geniuses only."],[2911,3048,"We don't accept frauds."],[3065,3244,"Plus, like you said,"],[3269,3357,"only the winner"],[3357,3478,"will be offered a position."],[3478,3632,"I never plagiarized anyone."],[3666,3791,"But of course I understand"],[3791,3916,"that empty words aren't enough."],[3941,4033,"In seven days,"],[4054,4204,"I'm going to prove my innocence."],[4204,4300,"I promise."],[4391,4571,"Miss, you need to do more"],[4642,4783,"than just prove your innocence."],[4833,4996,"You have to win the competition."],[5109,5317,"Are you that sure you can beat Olivia?"],[5380,5442,"Of course, sir."],[5530,5622,"Why would I be scared of"],[5622,5709,"that copycat?"],[5734,5830,"I've already thought of a way"],[5830,5939,"to expose her lies."],[5989,6072,"Just wait and see."]],"31":[[12,108,"I've already thought of a way"],[108,221,"to expose her lies."],[254,346,"Just wait and see."],[408,513,"I look forward to it."],[930,1042,"Well, I'll leave you to it."],[1096,1197,"Until next time, sir."],[1288,1372,"Mr. Smith."],[1372,1551,"After checking Olivia's code,"],[1601,1751,"we think she would be"],[1751,1856,"the perfect addition"],[1856,1972,"to the Quanta Project."],[1981,2077,"Just take a look at her-"],[2077,2223,"Thanks, but I already"],[2223,2385,"have a candidate in mind."],[2464,2594,"So soon?"],[2627,2706,"Wonderful."],[2723,2894,"I'll notify Olivia right away."],[2923,3028,"Not so fast."],[3057,3219,"The candidate I have in mind"],[3236,3324,"isn't Olivia."],[3616,3699,"It's Emily."],[3741,3803,"Emily?"],[3853,3908,"But sir,"],[3908,4087,"Emily is still under investigation"],[4087,4183,"for plagiarism."],[4204,4375,"There would be public outrage"],[4375,4483,"if she was chosen."],[4508,4683,"Jared, you can't take things"],[4683,4783,"at face value."],[4804,4909,"You gotta dig deeper."],[4954,5109,"Emily's the real genius here."],[5163,5221,"But..."],[5321,5388,"What?"],[5434,5509,"Don't sweat it."],[5526,5638,"Even if I tried to explain,"],[5638,5734,"you wouldn't understand."],[5759,5839,"Just wait."],[5839,6089,"In seven days, it'll all make sense."]],"32":[[308,379,"Emily!"],[379,521,"Olivia Hendricks just publicly"],[521,604,"accused you of plagiarizing"],[604,684,"her code."],[684,821,"What do you have to say for yourself?"],[829,988,"Is it true this wasn't your first time"],[988,1063,"appropriating someone"],[1063,1180,"else's accomplishments?"],[1197,1288,"Did you earn the title"],[1288,1405,"\"Genius Ghost Hacker\""],[1405,1564,"just by being a serial plagiarizer?"],[1564,1614,"You know,"],[1664,1818,"everyone's accusing me of plagiarism,"],[1818,1926,"but where's the proof?"],[1926,1985,"You're all supposed"],[1985,2093,"to be journalists, right?"],[2131,2260,"Instead of covering real stories,"],[2260,2352,"you're here trying to smear"],[2352,2452,"my reputation."],[2452,2594,"You will be hearing from my lawyer."],[2594,2736,"No, we spoke to contacts"],[2736,2786,"at your school"],[2786,2907,"that said this is not the first time"],[2907,3040,"that you plagiarized Olivia."],[3065,3236,"They said your code has been identical"],[3236,3328,"every time."],[3336,3520,"Are you still refusing to admit that?"],[3553,3749,"First, you copied her at school."],[3770,3920,"And now, you're trying to steal"],[3920,4049,"her hacker champion title."],[4049,4237,"Emily, do you have a personal vendetta"],[4237,4316,"against Olivia?"]],"33":[[25,120,"This is not the first time"],[120,258,"that you've plagiarized Olivia."],[258,408,"They said your code has been identical"],[408,500,"every time."],[500,600,"Are you still refusing to admit that?"],[600,809,"See, Emily, it doesn't matter"],[809,934,"if you've never plagiarized"],[934,1055,"in your life."],[1101,1263,"Everyone's taking my side."],[1276,1476,"In one week, we'll be holding a rematch"],[1476,1618,"of the Hacker Championships."],[1689,1780,"We'll be competing to see"],[1780,1976,"who can finish the final firewall code."],[2006,2127,"And if I lose,"],[2156,2239,"I will publicly"],[2239,2385,"admit to plagiarizing Olivia."],[2402,2485,"Is this the camera?"],[2548,2744,"Olivia, I'm challenging you"],[2744,2852,"to a rematch."],[2911,2998,"You said you could finish"],[2998,3094,"the final code, right?"],[3132,3290,"Well, then come prove it."],[3378,3566,"Oh, and get well soon."],[3603,3699,"We wouldn't want to have any"],[3699,3866,"health issues pop up next week."],[3895,3953,"Would we?"]],"34":[[137,283,"Bad news, Mr. Smith."],[283,442,"People on the Internet"],[442,654,"are bashing Emily after her interview."],[654,842,"Now she's hated for her plagiarism"],[842,1001,"and her smug attitude."],[1055,1205,"Sir, please reconsider"],[1205,1305,"your decision."],[1322,1430,"If the public finds out"],[1430,1530,"you want to put her"],[1530,1643,"on board the project,"],[1685,1772,"we're done for."],[1793,1868,"What do you mean?"],[1889,2043,"Her plagiarism accusations"],[2043,2114,"are trending on"],[2114,2281,"every social media platform."],[2335,2573,"Her reputation is in shambles."],[2602,2648,"If you let"],[2648,2836,"a controversial figure like this"],[2836,2994,"onto the Quanta Project,"],[3007,3082,"you'll be putting"],[3082,3290,"both the competition committee"],[3290,3495,"and your research team in hot water."],[3591,3795,"In one week, we'll be holding a rematch..."],[3816,3995,"Under a siege of reporters,"],[3995,4091,"she held her ground."],[4200,4387,"Instead of getting defensive,"],[4450,4571,"she managed to challenge"],[4571,4642,"the other party"],[4642,4800,"and stir up public opinion."],[4921,4992,"Not bad."],[5100,5192,"Not bad?"],[5234,5380,"What on earth do you mean?"],[5380,5484,"It's brilliant."],[5484,5601,"She leveraged media hype"],[5601,5705,"to garner international"],[5705,5797,"attention."],[5826,6010,"The whole world's watching her now."],[6022,6081,"She'll squash"],[6081,6247,"the plagiarism accusations"],[6247,6468,"and restore her reputation"],[6468,6598,"in one fell swoop."],[6681,6831,"But what if she fails?"],[6856,7019,"Trust me, she won't."]],"35":[[283,392,"Shit, shit, shit."],[392,487,"What am I gonna do?"],[542,667,"The rematch is in a week."],[784,946,"What if Emily tries to trip me up again"],[946,1092,"with those stupid songs?"],[1197,1405,"We wish you a merry Christmas."],[1405,1630,"We wish you a merry Christmas."],[1714,1910,"What's going on?"],[2010,2085,"Emily's acting like"],[2085,2210,"a whole different person."],[2260,2356,"Hurry up, she's here!"],[2364,2431,"Olivia!"],[2464,2627,"Emily challenged you to a rematch"],[2627,2711,"in seven days."],[2711,2857,"Are you confident you'll win"],[2861,3044,"or are you the real plagiarizer here?"],[3057,3111,"Yes, Miss."],[3111,3165,"Tell us the truth."],[3165,3303,"Everyone's dying to know."],[3303,3449,"Are you the hacker genius"],[3449,3545,"or the copycat?"]],"36":[[20,108,"Please, Miss Olivia,"],[108,229,"just a quick statement."],[654,792,"What the hell are you doing here?"],[792,859,"Get out!"],[900,996,"Quit filming."],[996,1096,"Shut it off."],[1096,1226,"Why won't you answer us, Olivia?"],[1226,1347,"Is it because you're guilty?"],[1964,2077,"Oh, sweetheart."],[2077,2185,"Were you scared?"],[2243,2318,"Olivia."],[2444,2510,"You okay?"],[2606,2886,"Mom, Dad, you're finally here."],[2973,3165,"What has gotten into those reporters?"],[3178,3332,"They think they can just walk up in here"],[3332,3507,"and accuse Olivia of plagiarism?"],[3507,3645,"I mean, she's the real cheater."],[3666,3762,"And now she thinks she can get"],[3762,3974,"a free pass by accusing Olivia?"],[3974,4145,"God, how did it all get so"],[4145,4229,"turned around?"],[4229,4371,"Ethan, don't be mad."],[4421,4667,"It's my fault for being so stupid."],[4708,4829,"I'm the one who passed out"],[4829,4967,"at the critical moment."],[4967,5146,"Oh, sweetheart."],[5159,5321,"Don't blame yourself."],[5342,5518,"Olivia, I've got an idea."],[5538,5680,"Why don't you finish writing the code"],[5680,5759,"for Challenge B"],[5759,5910,"and I'll publish it online?"],[5943,6060,"Then everyone will know that"],[6060,6193,"Emily is the real copycat."],[6272,6423,"Damien certainly has a point."],[6452,6564,"You're in the spotlight right now."],[6564,6760,"The earlier you can publish the code,"],[6844,6956,"the sooner we can clear up"],[6956,7090,"this whole media storm."],[7169,7319,"Well, good thing I brought my laptop."],[7461,7507,"Here."],[7670,7782,"Write the last part of the code."],[8028,8078,"Come on."],[8821,8938,"How the hell am I supposed to know"],[8938,9050,"what the final code is?"],[9050,9255,"Every time I try to read Emily's mind,"],[9255,9346,"she's singing those"],[9346,9484,"dumb Christmas songs."],[9538,9609,"Olivia."],[9663,9784,"Don't get distracted."],[9851,9926,"Come on."],[9926,10047,"Write the code."]],"37":[[187,246,"The..."],[604,884,"The final code is..."],[1526,1576,"Ow!"],[1605,1697,"My head."],[1772,1893,"Olivia, what's wrong?"],[2047,2135,"Get the doctor."],[2135,2227,"Doctor, help!"],[2373,2527,"Sir, what's going on with my sister?"],[2573,2711,"Well, according to the test results,"],[2711,2811,"she's completely fine."],[2836,2894,"Fine?"],[2919,3082,"Then why does her head still hurt?"],[3082,3203,"Has she experienced anything"],[3203,3382,"particularly stressful recently?"],[3382,3545,"Her migraines could be caused"],[3545,3724,"by extreme emotional distress."],[3774,3858,"If she continues"],[3858,3937,"resting for a few days,"],[3937,4008,"she should improve."],[4158,4358,"This is all because of Emily."],[4383,4450,"She's been putting"],[4450,4542,"all this pressure on Olivia"],[4542,4650,"and now look what's happened."],[4650,4821,"Emily's still salty as ever."],[4888,4971,"She's just jealous"],[4971,5171,"because Olivia's the real genius"],[5171,5284,"and a perfect sister."],[5284,5459,"Two things Emily will never be."],[5459,5543,"Call her right now."],[5543,5622,"Have her get here"],[5622,5772,"and apologize to Olivia."],[5964,6056,"Perfect."],[6072,6206,"We're not competing right now,"],[6222,6385,"so Emily won't be on high alert."],[6427,6631,"As long as I can get her within six feet,"],[6631,6740,"I can read her mind"],[6740,6906,"and take her code for myself."]],"38":[[45,125,"Forget it, Dad."],[162,308,"Don't be so hard on Emily."],[325,487,"I'm not in the right headspace now"],[487,579,"to compete anyway."],[629,692,"No."],[800,867,"You've been coding"],[867,1001,"day and night all these years"],[1001,1172,"just to bring pride to the Hendricks name."],[1201,1301,"We can't just sit back"],[1301,1426,"and let Emily tear you down."],[1430,1651,"But the competition's only a week away."],[1672,1830,"And Olivia gets migraines"],[1830,2022,"every time she thinks about it."],[2043,2248,"She's not in any shape to compete."],[2248,2356,"No, no, no, no."],[2356,2544,"Olivia, first place belongs to you."],[2544,2706,"I can't let Emily get her way."],[2915,2965,"Wait!"],[3003,3199,"Damien, just calm down for a second!"],[3645,3807,"How can Olivia read my mind?"],[3928,3999,"It seems like she has to be"],[3999,4158,"within a certain distance to do it."],[4195,4358,"As long as I can trigger the logic"],[4358,4479,"linked to the existing code"],[4479,4554,"in your brain,"],[4554,4679,"I can copy everything."],[5242,5330,"Come to the hospital"],[5330,5513,"and apologize to Olivia right now!"],[5513,5684,"You want me to apologize to her?"],[5684,5772,"Don't you think you should"],[5772,5914,"after abusing her like this?"],[5943,6089,"You're unbelievable, Emily."],[6114,6222,"If you don't come to the hospital"],[6222,6297,"right now"],[6297,6377,"and apologize,"],[6393,6514,"I'll make sure you never write"],[6514,6639,"a single line of code again."],[6710,6881,"I bet Olivia put him up to this."],[6911,7065,"The clueless idiot doesn't even know"],[7065,7194,"his pick-me sister"],[7194,7340,"is running circles around him."],[7386,7649,"Wait, can Olivia read their minds too?"],[7745,7874,"Save yourself the trouble, Damien."],[7912,7995,"I'll be right there."],[8249,8358,"Just wait, Olivia."],[8412,8533,"I'm not done with you yet."]],"39":[[120,300,"Damien just talked to Emily."],[367,554,"She's coming here to apologize to you."],[554,817,"Mom, you guys really didn't have to."],[817,950,"After what she's done to you,"],[950,1059,"a simple apology"],[1059,1222,"is nowhere near enough."],[1255,1443,"See, what I would really like"],[1443,1543,"is for her to..."],[2156,2218,"To what?"],[2623,2886,"Now what kind of attitude is that?"],[2969,3211,"Emily, thank you for coming to see me."],[3232,3415,"I'm fine, but the doctor says"],[3415,3503,"my headaches were due to"],[3503,3649,"extreme stress."],[3699,3787,"I keep getting migraines"],[3787,3903,"every time I think about"],[3903,3995,"the competition."],[4049,4187,"It's nothing major, though."],[4220,4333,"Really, I'll be fine."],[4383,4508,"Migraines, huh?"],[4571,4767,"Olivia, our rematch is in seven days."],[4863,4913,"What happens"],[4913,5050,"if you still get your migraines then?"],[5171,5292,"You're just not gonna show up?"],[5305,5388,"Seriously?"],[5409,5518,"You're laughing?"],[5534,5680,"You're the one who caused"],[5680,5860,"Olivia's migraines in the first place."],[5860,6043,"And now you're only making it worse"],[6043,6210,"with this smarty pants attitude"],[6210,6281,"of yours."],[6435,6706,"Apologize to Olivia immediately."],[6731,6794,"Mom,"],[6861,6919,"Dad."],[6956,7086,"Don't yell at Emily."],[7115,7198,"It was hard enough"],[7198,7336,"to get her to come see me."],[7465,7524,"Aw."],[7553,7607,"Olivia."],[7620,7912,"Olivia, you're so thoughtful."]],"40":[[75,329,"We all know about Emily's temper, guys."],[329,538,"Let's just forget about the apology."],[600,700,"I'll get over it."],[767,1197,"Wow, Olivia, that is so very touching."],[1234,1305,"But you know what?"],[1347,1451,"Instead of wasting your time"],[1451,1559,"acting so fake,"],[1559,1655,"you really might want to start"],[1655,1776,"thinking about the rematch."],[1805,1914,"Unless, of course that is,"],[1914,2152,"you plan to use your little migraines"],[2152,2335,"as an excuse to get out of it."],[2394,2556,"How dare you!"],[2831,3132,"Olivia, how can you still defend her?"],[3232,3440,"Emily's shameless bad-mouthing"],[3440,3561,"has gone too far."],[3578,3753,"Emily, we're sisters."],[3770,3903,"It doesn't matter which one"],[3903,4024,"of us wins."],[4054,4095,"We'll make"],[4095,4200,"the Hendricks family proud-"],[4200,4245,"Stop."],[4300,4400,"Don't come close to me."],[4458,4550,"For all I know, you could faint"],[4550,4667,"and then pin it on me again."],[4717,4850,"And as for the apology,"],[4850,4979,"that should come from Olivia."],[5067,5109,"She's the one"],[5109,5263,"who accused me of plagiarism"],[5263,5330,"without any evidence"],[5330,5401,"and she couldn't even"],[5401,5509,"finish the final code."],[5572,5684,"What the hell are you talking about?"],[5701,5805,"Olivia's in the hospital"],[5805,5855,"because of you"],[5855,5935,"and you're still out here"],[5935,6110,"spewing all these excuses."],[6110,6185,"Seriously?"],[6214,6297,"How long are all of you"],[6297,6427,"gonna keep ignoring the truth?"],[6427,6560,"Why am I supposed to say sorry"],[6560,6681,"when she's the copycat?"],[6852,7073,"Because I'm your brother and I said so."],[7248,7332,"My brother?"],[7365,7424,"Would my brother"],[7424,7570,"beat up his real sister"],[7570,7707,"to defend an imposter?"]],"41":[[20,125,"No sister of mine"],[125,308,"would ever act like this."],[308,487,"Apologize to Olivia right this second"],[487,604,"or I'll beat you until you do."],[604,905,"Damien, don't fight Emily over me."],[1038,1142,"Alright, Emily."],[1217,1393,"I'll drop out of the competition"],[1438,1559,"and I won't blame you"],[1559,1668,"for plagiarizing me."],[1668,1785,"All you have to do"],[1814,2018,"is apologize to Damien,"],[2035,2156,"tell him you're sorry,"],[2177,2394,"and we can all turn the page, okay?"],[2535,2631,"It's my fault."],[2652,2798,"I let Olivia copy me"],[2798,2990,"and almost win the competition."],[3044,3207,"For that, I'm so sorry."],[3678,3732,"Did you really think"],[3732,3870,"I'd let you hit me a second time?"]],"42":[[25,187,"Emily, it's not that"],[187,337,"we don't want to believe you,"],[337,412,"it's just that"],[504,704,"you grew up as a foster kid."],[746,946,"You had no formal training."],[946,1096,"Does it really make sense"],[1096,1301,"that someone with your background"],[1301,1518,"would know how to hack a satellite?"],[1518,1605,"Exactly."],[1630,1864,"But our Olivia, on the other hand,"],[1864,2039,"was trained by the best coders"],[2039,2097,"in the country."],[2097,2243,"After all the time and money"],[2243,2456,"we've poured into her education,"],[2489,2719,"why would she ever copy you?"],[2719,2852,"Well you all seem to have a lot of faith"],[2852,2927,"in her abilities,"],[2927,3082,"so why don't we give her a chance"],[3082,3190,"to prove herself, huh?"],[3294,3611,"Here are the coding prompts"],[3611,3749,"from the previous years."],[3778,3908,"You can pick anyone you'd like."],[3962,4033,"And if you happen to"],[4033,4137,"finish the challenge,"],[4195,4320,"I'll hold a press conference"],[4366,4512,"and admit that I plagiarized you."]],"43":[[45,175,"I'll hold a press conference"],[196,350,"and admit that I plagiarized you."],[404,596,"That's a piece of cake for Olivia."],[663,788,"You think she's afraid of you?"],[880,1021,"Come on, show her what you got."],[1238,1322,"Go for it, Olivia."],[1322,1443,"Let's see if she still has the guts"],[1443,1609,"to copy you after you embarrass her"],[1609,1705,"in front of everyone."],[1730,1785,"Shit!"],[1793,1881,"I have no clue"],[1881,2052,"how to write any of this code."],[2052,2143,"What do I do?"],[2515,2573,"Ow!"],[2665,2740,"Ow!"],[2761,2877,"Olivia, are you okay?"],[3148,3365,"You took that laptop out on purpose,"],[3365,3424,"didn't you?"],[3449,3745,"We just told you, Olivia gets migraines"],[3745,3841,"when she thinks"],[3841,3978,"about the competition."],[4149,4312,"Are they so blind to the truth"],[4312,4437,"that they can't even see through"],[4437,4558,"her pathetic act?"],[4596,4729,"I'm not holding out hope"],[4729,4854,"for a family like this."],[5242,5392,"Ethan, she's not actually"],[5392,5505,"getting migraines."],[5547,5755,"She's avoiding all things coding"],[5755,5876,"so that she can keep the truth"],[5876,5960,"under wraps."],[5993,6126,"It's insane how all of you"],[6126,6193,"turn a blind eye"],[6193,6360,"to someone so obviously guilty."],[6523,6731,"God, all you ever think about"],[6731,6890,"is framing Olivia."],[6944,7148,"You're just a dirty little liar,"],[7148,7332,"desperate to rip our family apart."],[7374,7499,"I should have never"],[7499,7686,"brought you back from foster care."],[7741,7878,"No, you shouldn't have."],[7941,8041,"You never should have even"],[8041,8249,"given birth to me in the first place."],[8249,8370,"How dare you?"],[8404,8550,"Don't talk to your mother like that."],[8550,8666,"She's not my mother."],[8792,8888,"She's Olivia's."],[8983,9096,"So have fun with your"],[9096,9292,"perfect happy little family."]],"44":[[12,250,"Mom, cut Emily some slack."],[262,392,"When all is said and done,"],[408,517,"we're still family."],[525,642,"And we should want nothing"],[642,784,"but the best for each other."],[838,1013,"Olivia, you're the best,"],[1013,1155,"unlike someone."],[1843,2110,"Emily, I'll drop out of the rematch,"],[2110,2202,"tutor you,"],[2202,2377,"and share my knowledge with you."],[2427,2585,"So you can win first place."],[2623,2723,"You still don't know the code"],[2723,2831,"to hack the satellite, right?"],[2965,3090,"I'm within six feet."],[3090,3274,"So I can read your mind."],[3274,3428,"If I can get you to think about"],[3428,3582,"the final set of code,"],[3582,3778,"I can finally steal your thunder"],[3778,3949,"and trample you beneath my feet."],[4041,4170,"Why are you so close to me?"],[4396,4608,"Trying to steal my code again, huh?"],[4683,4792,"Just stop, Emily."],[4813,4979,"After everything you've done to Olivia,"],[4979,5080,"she's still nice enough"],[5080,5163,"to give you guidance."],[5163,5376,"You're just obsessed with this idea"],[5376,5613,"of cheating your code"],[5613,5714,"that you won't even see"],[5714,5830,"when she's being nice."],[5868,6039,"Emily, please don't get me wrong."],[6072,6252,"I genuinely want to help you out."],[6314,6573,"Olivia, I'm so sick of your shit."],[6589,6748,"You can't even solve challenge A,"],[6748,6835,"but you want to teach me"],[6835,6956,"how to do challenge B?"],[6981,7115,"You're just a dumb poser"],[7115,7186,"who can't code."],[7186,7315,"I'm not a dumb poser!"],[7528,7628,"And you think I can't code?"],[7628,7720,"I'll show you!"]],"45":[[75,196,"Oh, you'll show me, huh?"],[262,304,"Oh, wait."],[346,442,"I thought you were still"],[442,517,"getting migraines"],[517,654,"when you thought about coding."],[704,788,"Are they gone now?"],[788,896,"Can you code again?"],[988,1096,"So, Olivia."],[1126,1267,"You're feeling better, right?"],[1305,1409,"You can write some code?"],[1547,1676,"Oh, this is fantastic."],[1676,1772,"Now you can compete"],[1772,1931,"in next week's rematch."],[1947,2064,"Well, now that Olivia's headaches"],[2064,2139,"are gone,"],[2173,2314,"I think she's got first place"],[2314,2381,"in the bag."],[2444,2515,"Yeah."],[2590,2644,"Right."],[2644,2786,"It'll be easy peasy."],[2865,2961,"Damn it, Emily."],[2961,3119,"I thought you were cursing me out loud,"],[3119,3257,"but it was all in your head."],[3282,3395,"Congrats, Olivia."],[3424,3541,"Since you're feeling better,"],[3541,3645,"you're not getting migraines,"],[3645,3691,"do you think you can"],[3691,3787,"get me some pointers?"],[3841,3962,"I mean, you did say"],[3962,4045,"that you could help me"],[4045,4191,"with challenge B, right?"],[4258,4346,"I have been having"],[4346,4500,"a little bit of trouble with that code,"],[4500,4650,"so I would really appreciate the help."],[4704,4796,"Can we take a look?"],[4859,4950,"Damn it, Emily."],[4979,5146,"If you don't even know the code,"],[5146,5321,"how the hell am I supposed to help?"],[5409,5472,"Well..."],[5543,5684,"Miss Genius Hacker Girl,"],[5684,5868,"are you gonna wow me with your skills?"],[5972,6235,"Or is this all just Greek to you?"]],"46":[[12,116,"If my parents find out"],[116,275,"I can't actually write code,"],[275,375,"I'm finished!"],[375,521,"What are you talking about, Emily?"],[533,658,"Olivia writes high-level code"],[658,763,"in her sleep."],[763,842,"But come on,"],[842,925,"you're putting her on the spot."],[938,1038,"This is probably just another one"],[1038,1130,"of your schemes"],[1130,1267,"to accuse her of cheating."],[1267,1426,"Well, she said she'd tutor me."],[1426,1505,"Did she not?"],[1505,1626,"But on second thought,"],[1643,1843,"if you can't even finish challenge A,"],[1864,2039,"how are you gonna finish challenge B?"],[2064,2139,"Come on."],[2160,2285,"Give her a second to breathe."],[2285,2485,"Olivia hasn't even left the hospital yet,"],[2485,2660,"and here you are triggering her trauma"],[2660,2781,"by shoving this challenge"],[2781,2869,"in her face."],[2873,3053,"Just wait till she fully recovers,"],[3053,3174,"and then she'll tutor you."],[3174,3349,"I swear to God, Emily."],[3382,3524,"If Olivia's headaches come back"],[3524,3616,"because of you-"],[3616,3928,"Guys, let's not gang up on Emily."],[3987,4212,"I don't mind pushing myself a bit"],[4254,4396,"if it makes Emily happy."],[4637,4713,"I'll do it."],[5046,5150,"I'll write the code."]],"47":[[1443,1576,"How long are you going to"],[1576,1772,"keep tormenting poor Olivia?"],[1772,2010,"Mom, I told you not to blame Emily."],[2022,2168,"She just wants to win first place"],[2168,2277,"and gain your approval."],[2460,2573,"Don't worry, Emily."],[2590,2752,"I'll give up first place for you."],[2790,2823,"You know,"],[2823,2977,"if you really love acting so much,"],[3019,3103,"you should really try"],[3103,3240,"striking it out in Hollywood."]],"48":[[87,291,"Laying hands on your own mother?"],[371,633,"You are completely out of line."],[633,746,"Jesus, Emily."],[746,855,"I literally can't tell"],[855,971,"if you're a worse sister"],[971,1071,"or a worse daughter."],[1326,1401,"Are you out of your mind?"],[1401,1555,"Yes, I am."],[1555,1785,"All of you are driving me insane!"],[1801,1926,"If we knew you were gonna"],[1926,2022,"turn out like this,"],[2072,2189,"we would never"],[2189,2323,"let you step foot on this earth."],[2323,2448,"Well, isn't that a coincidence?"],[2448,2598,"I never wanted shitty parents"],[2598,2694,"like you two either."],[2831,2911,"You little-"],[2911,3140,"Dad, Emily didn't mean that."],[3174,3278,"Emily, just"],[3286,3482,"apologize to Mom and Dad,"],[3490,3607,"and I promise you"],[3607,3745,"I'll let the plagiarism thing slide."],[3745,3841,"Oh my God."],[3841,4004,"I will say it for the last time."],[4037,4179,"I never plagiarized you."],[4179,4279,"You are the one"],[4279,4379,"causing all of the problems"],[4379,4433,"in this family."],[4433,4554,"Everything that's gone wrong"],[4554,4637,"is because of you!"],[4637,4729,"If you think"],[4742,4896,"everything is my fault,"],[4896,4954,"then"],[5046,5125,"I'll leave."],[5209,5338,"I'll get out of your way."],[5359,5534,"For the greater good of the family."],[5880,5989,"That won't be necessary."],[6452,6519,"Sign this."],[6664,6731,"And all my ties"],[6731,6815,"with the Hendricks family"],[6815,6877,"will be cut."],[6877,7023,"You'll never have to speak to me again."],[7036,7207,"And I'll be out of the family for good."]],"49":[[33,250,"You want us to sever ties?"],[279,450,"Do you even know what you're saying?"],[475,696,"Emily, if word got out about this,"],[709,804,"the Hendricks family"],[804,921,"would be the laughingstock"],[921,1017,"of the nation."],[1038,1192,"Isn't that what you wanted though?"],[1251,1309,"With me gone,"],[1309,1526,"you all can live happily ever after"],[1526,1685,"with your golden daughter Olivia."],[1701,1801,"Besides, everyone's already"],[1801,1926,"calling me a plagiarizer."],[1993,2127,"So with me gone, you're not gonna"],[2127,2285,"destroy the family's reputation."],[2352,2419,"You'll save it."],[2419,2640,"Emily, just calm down a second."],[2711,2836,"Didn't I say I'd stop"],[2836,2969,"bugging you about the plagiarism?"],[3065,3240,"Besides, you're the real"],[3240,3349,"Hendricks heiress."],[3349,3566,"They're your biological family."],[3591,3757,"If there can only be one daughter"],[3757,3853,"in this family,"],[3933,4037,"then I'll leave."],[4179,4250,"Well, fine."],[4320,4400,"Go ahead."],[4487,4542,"Leave."]],"50":[[54,250,"Well, you seemed pretty determined"],[250,354,"just a second ago."],[408,571,"Another Oscar-winning"],[571,625,"performance"],[625,759,"from Olivia Hendricks."],[796,1076,"It's just so hard for me"],[1076,1192,"to leave you guys."],[1209,1472,"Olivia, don't cry."],[1526,1605,"No one in the family"],[1605,1685,"wants to kick you out."],[1685,1851,"She's clearly playing us."],[1851,2002,"This whole cutting ties thing"],[2002,2093,"is just a ploy"],[2093,2189,"to guilt-trip you"],[2189,2293,"and make you leave."],[2293,2448,"I can't believe I gave birth"],[2448,2606,"to such a spiteful daughter."],[2665,2756,"I'll sign this."],[3232,3324,"I'll sign it too."],[3415,3465,"Yeah."],[3682,3757,"Me as well."],[4471,4521,"Great."],[4733,4808,"Now, we have nothing to do"],[4808,4892,"with each other."],[5230,5301,"By the way,"],[5376,5476,"aren't you all curious"],[5476,5597,"how Olivia always seems"],[5597,5755,"to know exactly what we're thinking?"]],"51":[[33,129,"Aren't you all curious"],[129,250,"how Olivia always seems"],[250,396,"to know exactly what we're thinking?"],[734,792,"Emily?"],[875,1013,"What are you talking about?"],[1105,1242,"Olivia, let her go."],[1272,1355,"She's probably just hoping to"],[1355,1526,"drive one last wedge between us."],[1555,1801,"Guys, how is she gonna"],[1801,1922,"support herself out there"],[1922,2027,"all on her own?"],[2052,2218,"I mean, she doesn't even"],[2218,2356,"have her high school diploma."],[2356,2431,"Oh, who cares?"],[2452,2519,"It's high time"],[2519,2665,"she experienced the real world,"],[2677,2827,"that's the only way she'll understand"],[2827,3044,"just how much we have spoiled her."],[3044,3219,"God, what a rebellious brat."],[3236,3336,"I can't believe some of the things"],[3336,3424,"she was saying to us."],[3453,3574,"Listen, I don't want"],[3574,3720,"any one of you going after her."],[3791,3895,"Let her fend for herself."],[3912,3995,"Amen."],[4029,4204,"We treated her like royalty"],[4204,4471,"and all she ever did was sulk around."],[4629,4696,"Wait."],[4758,4984,"Once she is out in the real world,"],[4992,5134,"she'll come running back,"],[5159,5372,"begging for forgiveness."],[5413,5530,"Olivia, just focus on"],[5530,5643,"making a full recovery."],[5705,5830,"When Emily comes back,"],[5830,5976,"you'll finally get that apology"],[5976,6068,"you've been waiting for."]],"52":[[304,400,"Audrey!"],[513,754,"Go freeze all of Emily's credit cards."],[800,909,"And tell our accountants"],[909,1046,"not to give her a single cent"],[1046,1117,"from now on."],[1146,1330,"She wants to sever ties with us."],[1384,1547,"We're gonna make it a clean cut."],[1584,1801,"I apologize, Mr. and Mrs. Hendricks,"],[1801,1935,"but Miss Emily"],[1935,2102,"doesn't have any credit cards."],[2131,2256,"And our accountant"],[2256,2406,"has never given her any money."],[2431,2506,"What?"],[2640,2806,"Audrey, what do you mean?"],[3015,3103,"That's impossible."],[3161,3265,"I'm afraid it's true."],[3340,3674,"Miss Olivia, Damien, Ethan"],[3699,3866,"have always had credit cards"],[3866,3933,"and bank accounts"],[3933,4016,"under their name."],[4016,4304,"But Miss Emily, since living here,"],[4375,4542,"hasn't received as much as a penny."],[4646,4725,"Are you serious?"],[4871,4984,"How has she gotten by all these years"],[4984,5059,"without any money?"]],"53":[[8,95,"You mean,"],[154,425,"we haven't given her any money"],[425,533,"since we brought her back"],[533,700,"from the foster family?"],[917,1117,"Why didn't that rascal say anything?"],[1151,1238,"She's making us sound like"],[1238,1322,"we've been neglecting her"],[1322,1401,"on purpose."],[1422,1614,"Okay, so we forgot to"],[1614,1718,"give her an allowance."],[1718,1851,"But we let her live here."],[1868,1960,"And we kept her fed"],[1960,2102,"in this luxurious mansion."],[2122,2281,"All of that we gave her,"],[2310,2502,"and she's still ungrateful enough"],[2565,2698,"to cut ties with us?"],[2698,2865,"Um, actually,"],[2902,3032,"uh, never mind."],[3073,3169,"Just spit it out."],[3215,3436,"Ever since Miss Emily came here"],[3436,3541,"from the foster home,"],[3541,3716,"her living conditions"],[3716,3899,"haven't exactly been great."],[3949,4091,"What do you mean?"],[4992,5088,"What the hell?"],[5113,5284,"Our doghouse is bigger than this."],[5334,5526,"Miss Emily has been living in this room"],[5526,5630,"since she came back"],[5630,5739,"from the foster home."],[5780,6026,"That room has no A/C or heating."],[6039,6122,"You're telling me she's lived"],[6126,6256,"like this for five years?"],[6289,6418,"Even if we didn't always"],[6418,6527,"get along with her,"],[6527,6656,"we'd never treat her this badly"],[6656,6769,"on purpose."],[6798,6981,"How could there not be a single bedroom"],[6981,7115,"in this house for her to use?"],[7136,7294,"Who the hell decided this?"],[7444,7678,"It was you, Mrs. Hendricks."]],"54":[[12,191,"It sucks that Dior was closed today."],[191,321,"I really want to get a new perfume."],[321,396,"I know."],[396,446,"Next time"],[446,563,"I'll make an appointment"],[563,633,"with them."],[663,704,"I know."],[704,804,"I guess I still got a lot."],[821,871,"It's good."],[875,988,"Oh, yes."],[1021,1113,"Wow, Mom."],[1113,1234,"You bought me so many clothes."],[1234,1297,"I don't have anywhere"],[1297,1380,"to put them."],[1447,1589,"And my closet's packed."],[1589,1755,"Then how about we combine"],[1755,1985,"all the guest rooms on the second floor"],[1985,2052,"and turn them"],[2052,2227,"into a walk-in closet for you?"],[2248,2314,"Oh, Mom."],[2314,2427,"You're the best."],[2602,2690,"Mom, can I talk to you"],[2690,2748,"about something?"],[2915,3098,"My bedroom's kind of small."],[3111,3219,"Is it okay if I move into"],[3219,3340,"one of the guest rooms upstairs?"],[3374,3428,"Wait."],[3524,3611,"Mom, does this mean"],[3611,3766,"I don't get my new closet anymore?"],[3987,4049,"Are you mad"],[4049,4200,"that Mom's giving me a closet?"],[4241,4404,"Are you trying to take it from me?"],[4496,4700,"Emily, please."],[4700,4850,"We've had a long day,"],[4850,4959,"and the first thing you do"],[4959,5038,"is pick a fight"],[5038,5230,"with your sister over a room?"],[5263,5321,"What?"],[5334,5438,"Are you going to fight"],[5438,5538,"over your inheritance"],[5538,5643,"in the future, too?"],[5826,6010,"You really disappoint me, Emily."],[6064,6135,"Mom, I..."],[6256,6431,"Could you close the door?"]],"55":[[12,129,"It was me."],[254,429,"I'm the one who made her live here."],[500,625,"I thought Emily was just"],[625,750,"picking a fight with Olivia,"],[750,925,"so I didn't let her change her room."],[1046,1184,"I misunderstood her."],[1192,1309,"Then why didn't she come to me?"],[1334,1426,"She could have told me"],[1426,1526,"instead of living in this dump"],[1526,1647,"for five whole years."],[2014,2097,"I remember."],[2168,2239,"Yes, sir."],[2260,2481,"Miss Emily did ask, but-"],[2502,2594,"I turned her down."],[2731,2844,"I didn't want Olivia to feel like"],[2844,2965,"we were favoring Emily."],[2986,3123,"But I didn't know she was living here."],[3307,3499,"Hey, aren't those the coats"],[3499,3620,"we told Emily to throw out?"],[4062,4124,"Hey, wait."],[4158,4225,"What are you guys doing"],[4225,4304,"with those clothes?"],[4337,4446,"Tossing them out."],[4466,4529,"Duh."],[4550,4654,"Why are you tossing them?"],[4654,4738,"That's such a waste."],[4884,4954,"Can I keep them?"],[5100,5180,"She's been using"],[5180,5347,"those old coats as blankets?"],[5438,5559,"We neglected her."],[5576,5668,"No wonder she wanted to"],[5668,5789,"cut all ties with us."],[5897,6089,"We've let her down so many times."],[6101,6160,"Dad."],[6289,6343,"Mom."],[6368,6481,"The rematch is in a week."],[6510,6656,"We'll see Emily there."],[6685,6865,"As long as she apologizes"],[6865,7052,"and admits that she copied Olivia,"],[7065,7165,"we'll take her back."],[7273,7357,"Make it up to her."]],"56":[[179,258,"Mr. Smith?"],[258,342,"Miss Emily. - Hi."],[387,504,"What brings you to my office?"],[504,638,"The competition is about to start."],[638,738,"Shouldn't you be prepping?"],[775,871,"Or are you that confident"],[871,996,"you can beat Miss Olivia?"],[1030,1259,"Well, beating her is easier"],[1259,1409,"than taking candy from a baby."],[1497,1626,"You seem pretty sure of yourself."],[1639,1793,"Well, I guess I'll be waiting"],[1793,1910,"for your good news."],[1910,2010,"Actually, sir."],[2081,2206,"There's something I wanted to ask you"],[2206,2331,"before the competition starts."],[2435,2652,"Have you heard of mind reading?"],[3123,3203,"Let me show you."],[3703,3949,"This time, I'm ending Olivia for good."],[3987,4083,"No comebacks."],[4104,4237,"No second chances."]],"57":[[41,196,"Everyone, welcome back"],[196,379,"to the Hackers Championship."],[400,525,"Stay tuned to find out"],[525,717,"who will take home first place."],[759,959,"And now, let's welcome back"],[959,1151,"our participants to the stage."],[1739,1868,"Just looking at her"],[1868,1972,"reminds me of everything"],[1972,2047,"we've done wrong."],[2064,2193,"We never gave her a cent,"],[2193,2419,"shoved her into that storage room."],[2419,2552,"We really failed her."],[2581,2798,"Look, it's not all on us, okay?"],[2798,2932,"Emily's always been difficult."],[2961,3128,"If she had just met us halfway"],[3128,3232,"every once in a while,"],[3286,3395,"it wouldn't have come to this."],[3465,3586,"That's weird."],[3586,3778,"Why is Emily, the plagiarist,"],[3778,3912,"the only person up there?"],[3962,4049,"Where's Olivia?"],[4049,4208,"Hey, they still haven't proven"],[4208,4387,"who the real plagiarizer is."],[4404,4587,"But maybe Olivia's too scared"],[4587,4675,"to show up."],[4704,4792,"This is it."],[4838,5000,"My only chance to clear my name"],[5000,5201,"and take back everything I've lost."],[5246,5438,"If Miss Olivia isn't here,"],[5509,5914,"then by default, the winner is-"],[5914,5980,"Wait!"]],"58":[[70,125,"It's you."],[141,212,"For a minute there,"],[212,329,"I thought you weren't gonna show up."],[329,558,"Emily, I know you want to win"],[558,633,"first place."],[654,771,"But winning this competition"],[771,934,"is also my dream."],[934,1080,"And after some persuading"],[1080,1176,"from the family,"],[1222,1393,"I've decided to go all out."],[1405,1493,"I'm not just gonna"],[1493,1589,"hand first place to you"],[1589,1714,"just because you're my sister."],[1747,1860,"I won't waste"],[1860,1997,"our parents' investment in me."],[2035,2193,"Well, let's just hope"],[2193,2273,"you don't fake another"],[2273,2364,"fainting spell again."],[2435,2506,"Good luck."],[2506,2615,"I wasn't faking."],[2715,2907,"I just didn't want to embarrass you"],[2907,3053,"for the sake of our parents."],[3053,3207,"But I passed out because of"],[3207,3357,"how aggressive you were being."],[3420,3712,"But since you've cut ties with my family,"],[3787,3866,"I've got nothing"],[3866,3983,"holding me back anymore."],[4083,4304,"I will show no mercy this time."],[4329,4391,"Really?"],[4483,4692,"You really think you can finish the code?"],[4717,4821,"Just wait and see."],[4842,4979,"We're both under fire for this"],[4979,5105,"plagiarism scandal, right?"],[5176,5267,"Let's settle it."],[5292,5463,"Whoever finishes the code first"],[5463,5651,"will prove that they're the real deal."],[5651,5905,"And, if we write the same exact thing,"],[5947,6076,"then it's obvious"],[6076,6235,"that you've been copying me."],[6260,6414,"How could I copy you?"],[6414,6481,"Whatever."],[6481,6569,"Be my guest."],[6619,6790,"I'm dying to see what you come up with."]],"59":[[2010,2122,"How is this possible?"],[2469,2648,"How are you writing the rest of the code?"],[3440,3499,"There."],[3557,3745,"That's my code to hack the satellite."],[3745,3858,"Satellite firewall"],[3858,3995,"successfully breached."]],"60":[[29,187,"I made sure to keep my mind clear."],[221,279,"There's no way"],[279,375,"she could have read my mind"],[375,517,"and have overheard my thoughts."],[575,642,"How did she..."],[704,788,"Why is your code"],[788,946,"exactly the same as mine?"],[1001,1172,"Get out of here, you fraud!"],[1184,1343,"Why is this copycat"],[1343,1576,"accusing Olivia again?"],[1597,1776,"Literally everyone here saw it."],[1797,1972,"Olivia hacked the satellite first."],[1981,2239,"God, Emily's still the same."],[2273,2364,"That's why everyone's"],[2364,2431,"sick of her."],[2485,2660,"Emily, give it up already."],[2681,2761,"How long are you gonna"],[2761,2882,"keep accusing Olivia?"],[2907,2977,"Oh my God!"],[2977,3178,"She's embarrassing our entire family."],[3282,3428,"Just apologize."],[3457,3557,"But off the stage."],[3557,3649,"Didn't you say"],[3649,3778,"if I could finish the code,"],[3778,3895,"then you'd apologize?"],[3933,4029,"Go on, Emily."],[4054,4145,"Keep your word."],[4479,4571,"Fraud."],[4596,4758,"Boo!"],[4758,4821,"Ugh!"],[4821,4925,"Ugh, copycat!"],[4925,5092,"That's the rest of my code!"],[5092,5217,"She copied me!"],[5259,5388,"What an idiot."],[5417,5630,"The more you argue, the worse you look."],[5663,5789,"No one's gonna believe you."],[5789,6064,"Emily, I've let it slide every time"],[6064,6210,"you've accused me of plagiarism."],[6256,6377,"But this time,"],[6377,6589,"I proved in front of everyone"],[6589,6760,"that I wrote the code first."],[6919,7203,"So tell me, how could I have copied you?"]],"61":[[4,116,"You're the worst."],[158,321,"Boo!"],[321,383,"Ugh!"],[383,513,"Ugh, copycat!"],[513,571,"Please,"],[613,775,"everyone, you have to believe me."],[775,913,"I am innocent."],[930,1109,"The last time they were even together"],[1109,1251,"was at the hospital."],[1251,1451,"We've never seen Emily"],[1451,1622,"write anything this complex."],[1622,1722,"There's no way"],[1722,1881,"Olivia could have copied her."],[1922,2193,"Why does Emily always target her?"],[2206,2448,"She's been smearing Olivia"],[2460,2627,"in front of a global audience."],[2648,2686,"Okay."],[2686,2827,"Repeatedly plagerizing"],[2827,2936,"and framing her."],[3044,3136,"She deserves whatever's"],[3136,3224,"coming at her."],[3553,3707,"Well, I guess this means"],[3707,3862,"Olivia is the winner"],[3862,4016,"of the Hacker Championships."],[4045,4262,"Emily, once you're proven guilty,"],[4262,4396,"no one will believe you."],[4421,4612,"No matter how talented you are,"],[4642,4825,"you'll stay beneath me forever."],[4909,5063,"How did she even copy me?"],[5092,5230,"Emily, if you can't finish"],[5230,5292,"the last code,"],[5292,5384,"just let me know."],[5438,5555,"I'd be glad to help you out"],[5555,5676,"in light of our past sisterhood."],[5676,5797,"I don't need your help."],[5868,5980,"I can finish it myself."],[6010,6202,"Then please, go ahead."],[6527,6719,"Olivia's got this in the bag."],[6806,6952,"Go tell the media to release"],[6952,7052,"a statement now."],[7102,7211,"Olivia's already won."],[7248,7344,"Hold on, Dad."],[7390,7524,"Don't pop the champagne yet."],[7578,7770,"Emily hasn't even started coding."]],"62":[[842,913,"Look at her."],[942,1042,"She's not even moving."],[1113,1226,"I bet she can't finish it."],[1422,1514,"Do we have to stay here until"],[1514,1626,"the timer runs out?"],[1626,1689,"At this point,"],[1689,1814,"she won't even write a single line"],[1814,1956,"until after the competition."],[1981,2064,"She should've admitted to"],[2064,2256,"plagiarizing and apologized to Olivia"],[2256,2323,"earlier."],[2548,2598,"Look!"],[2740,2865,"She's typing now."],[3249,3349,"This is impossible."],[3370,3499,"There's no way she could come up"],[3499,3653,"with a new approach this fast."],[3903,4062,"Why is Emily's code"],[4062,4212,"identical to Olivia's?"],[4229,4391,"Is she actually copying"],[4391,4483,"Olivia's work?"],[4500,4688,"She's actually rewriting my code"],[4688,4792,"in front of everyone."],[4792,4900,"And you still wonder why"],[4900,5038,"people call you a copycat?"],[5075,5201,"What an idiot!"],[5201,5305,"How shameless."],[5355,5513,"Olivia already wrote the code."],[5559,5663,"She's copying it"],[5697,5797,"so blatantly."],[5822,5968,"Does she think we're stupid?"],[5993,6164,"Get out of here, you copycat!"],[6197,6293,"Get out of here!"],[6368,6464,"Leave!"],[6527,6635,"You don't belong here!"],[6673,6744,"Cheater!"],[6794,6906,"Satellite firewall"],[6906,7036,"successfully breached."],[7036,7132,"Here's my code."]],"63":[[8,191,"Emily, what are you talking about?"],[191,354,"You just copied my work."],[379,462,"Seriously?"],[538,696,"You're trying to say again"],[696,809,"that I copied you?"],[809,1001,"I didn't want to say it like that,"],[1021,1222,"but everyone saw it."],[1234,1347,"Emily, that's enough."],[1347,1505,"We all just saw you copy Olivia."],[1526,1622,"You think we're idiots?"],[1622,1876,"I actually regretted neglecting you."],[1914,2064,"I was ready to take you back"],[2077,2252,"if you just owned up to it."],[2252,2506,"But you really let me down today."],[2606,2748,"Apologize to Olivia."],[2857,2957,"Look closely."],[2957,3015,"Apologize."],[3015,3232,"My process isn't the same as Olivia's."],[3232,3328,"What makes you all think"],[3328,3507,"you can keep calling me a plagiarizer?"],[3807,3895,"It's true."],[3920,4066,"Emily's coding steps"],[4066,4216,"are different from Olivia's."],[4216,4366,"Wait, what's going on?"],[4366,4550,"Can someone give us an explanation?"],[6881,7086,"After reviewing both sets of code,"],[7215,7303,"I've decided."],[7394,7561,"The winner of this year's"],[7561,7778,"Hacker Championship is..."]],"64":[[8,204,"The winner of this year's"],[204,412,"Hacker Championship is..."],[809,880,"Emily!"],[1267,1539,"Boo!"],[1539,1626,"Cheater!"],[1626,1801,"Wait, how is this possible?"],[1801,2018,"Wasn't Emily the one plagiarizing Olivia?"],[2064,2268,"There's definitely something off here."],[2285,2594,"Boo!"],[2619,2744,"Boo!"],[2744,2902,"Everyone, settle down."],[2969,3119,"We've taken the plagiarism scandal"],[3119,3211,"very seriously."],[3219,3328,"Thanks to Emily,"],[3340,3482,"we've finally uncovered the truth."],[3532,3674,"We've found the real culprit."],[3707,3774,"Emily,"],[3807,3962,"what is going on here?"],[3962,4049,"Let me explain."],[4200,4333,"Yesterday, Emily came to me"],[4333,4579,"with her own version of the final code."],[4604,4729,"But to confirm the truth,"],[4729,4904,"we sent one of our organizers"],[4959,5313,"to drop a USB drive to Olivia's hospital"],[5313,5413,"where we make her think"],[5426,5522,"it was Emily's."],[5522,5805,"That USB contained a sample version"],[5805,5914,"of the final code."],[5935,6001,"Are you saying that"],[6001,6143,"Olivia copied the USB?"],[6185,6289,"That's ridiculous."],[6306,6452,"The facts speak for themselves."],[6760,6873,"Syetem error."],[6940,7077,"Operation failed."],[7157,7332,"Initiating code purge."],[7386,7565,"Ocean 2 Satellite accessed."],[7653,7811,"Please input next steps."]],"65":[[50,241,"Ocean 2 Satellite accessed."],[321,471,"Please input next steps."],[567,829,"While Olivia's code did breach"],[855,980,"the satellite firewall."],[1042,1247,"It never really actually hacked"],[1292,1455,"the satellite control system."],[1493,1651,"That's because her code"],[1664,1943,"was a direct copy of the one on the USB."],[2018,2131,"In that code,"],[2173,2373,"Emily shuffled a few random lines"],[2373,2477,"and deliberately"],[2477,2652,"added some random lines of code."],[2815,3015,"I didn't think Olivia would match"],[3015,3307,"the USB down to those random lines."],[3357,3470,"You set me up!"],[3566,3766,"Well, you can't fake genius."],[3803,4120,"It takes real talent and real hard work."],[4258,4542,"Unless you can read minds."],[4821,5117,"You know everything?"],[5213,5355,"No wonder you were singing"],[5355,5492,"those stupid Christmas songs"],[5492,5593,"in your head last time."],[5643,5780,"You did it on purpose!"]],"66":[[120,175,"Wait."],[233,442,"Why can't I read your mind right now?"],[575,658,"Looking for this?"],[959,1126,"What are they even talking about?"],[1126,1317,"Ever wonder how Olivia managed"],[1317,1568,"to copy me so perfectly every time,"],[1568,1718,"even during Challenge A?"],[1793,2052,"Dad, did she catch on?"],[2202,2377,"It's all because of this."],[2427,2594,"This is not a normal accessory."],[2606,2686,"It's actually"],[2686,2852,"a brainwave transmitter."],[2961,3123,"After an investigation,"],[3136,3315,"I discovered that the Hendricks family"],[3353,3524,"has been forcing homeless people"],[3524,3749,"into brutal and illegal"],[3749,3903,"neurotech experiments."],[4800,4967,"How on earth did she find out?"],[5013,5109,"We kept this experiment"],[5109,5155,"under wraps,"],[5155,5267,"not even Olivia knew."],[5292,5492,"After decades of experiments,"],[5530,5655,"the transmitter eventually"],[5655,5860,"evolved into this hair clip you see here."],[5860,5993,"As long as I wear it,"],[5993,6135,"Olivia can read my mind"],[6202,6519,"and steal my code."],[6602,6765,"But everyone involved"],[6765,6877,"in these experiments"],[6877,7048,"eventually lost their minds"],[7052,7182,"and took their own lives."],[7912,8158,"Was I just another lab rat to you?"],[8450,8512,"Why?"]],"67":[[145,387,"Just as the experiment"],[387,533,"was in its final stages,"],[546,767,"those stupid, weak test subjects"],[767,884,"started killing themselves"],[884,980,"one after another."],[1005,1096,"It was frustrating."],[1121,1322,"But we were too close"],[1322,1463,"to success to stop."],[1488,1747,"And after investing billions"],[1747,1868,"into this research,"],[1868,2081,"it is finally paying off."],[2114,2306,"We will not let you to ruin this."],[2423,2556,"You want to be our golden child?"],[2573,2648,"Then you're gonna do"],[2648,2748,"as you're told to do."],[2769,2915,"And sacrifice!"],[3194,3357,"I used to mock you"],[3390,3599,"for being the unwanted orphan."],[3603,3728,"But I'm no better,"],[3728,3799,"am I?"],[4091,4145,"Ow!"],[4145,4241,"My head."],[4283,4375,"It hurts."],[4746,4854,"And now Emily!"],[4896,5080,"I'm their favorite daughter!"],[5163,5301,"They love me!"],[5526,5734,"She hasn't even won the competition"],[5734,5885,"and she's already losing it."],[5922,6085,"She's useless now."],[6118,6243,"Turns out she's a victim"],[6243,6377,"of the experiment too."],[6389,6552,"And they're the ones who ruined her."]],"68":[[246,433,"The Hendricks family has been arrested"],[433,521,"under suspicion"],[521,721,"of illegal human experiments."],[742,942,"Olivia Hendricks, deeply involved"],[942,1080,"in the plagiarism scandal,"],[1096,1184,"is now confirmed"],[1184,1322,"to be one of their victims."],[1347,1543,"After suffering a mental breakdown,"],[1543,1643,"she's been committed"],[1643,1826,"to a psychiatric institution."],[1893,2118,"As for the Hacker Championships,"],[2147,2310,"the winner is..."],[2439,2635,"Welcome to the Quanta Project."],[2635,2740,"Thank you, Mr. Smith."],[2740,2890,"This is a dream come true."],[2998,3078,"Emily!"],[3115,3365,"I'm telling you, they love me!"],[3365,3595,"I'm their favorite daughter, bitch!"],[3628,3741,"What are you gonna do about her?"],[3753,4033,"Well, they say that life often"],[4033,4166,"reflects one's childhood."],[4275,4425,"People who grew up feeling unloved"],[4425,4542,"often will spend their whole lives"],[4542,4596,"trying to prove"],[4596,4700,"that someone does love them."],[4733,4813,"And what about you?"],[4904,5063,"I can't let the past chain me down,"],[5063,5117,"you know?"],[5213,5342,"I gotta keep my eyes forward."],[5459,5601,"Too much world out there to see."],[5714,5818,"Too much left to do."]]}